#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:378
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:379
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:380
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:381
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:382
msgid "Tentacle"
msgstr "Tentacule"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:824
msgid "Ack! What are those things!"
msgstr "Beurk ! Qu'est-ce que c'est que ces choses ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:835
msgid ""
"Oh yeah, those things. Watch out, they are the arms of some sort of "
"underwater creature. They'll try to pummel you to death, then drag you under "
"for dinner."
msgstr ""
"Ah oui, ces choses. Prenez garde, ce sont les bras d'une espèce de créature "
"sous-marine. Ils sont là pour vous tuer puis vous tirer au fond pour le "
"dîner."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:840
msgid ""
"Then how do we get past? I can see that the passage continues to both the "
"north and south and we haven't found Malifor yet..."
msgstr ""
"Alors comment allons-nous passer ? Apparemment, le passage se poursuit au "
"nord et au sud et nous n'avons toujours pas trouvé Malifor..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:845
msgid ""
"Creatures of that type regenerate over time; it's doubtful we can destroy it "
"completely. But if we destroy its arms we'll be relatively safe until they "
"regenerate."
msgstr ""
"Eh bien, les créatures de ce genre se régénèrent avec le temps donc je doute "
"fort que nous puissions la détruire complètement. Mais en détruisant ses "
"bras, nous devrions être tranquilles pour un moment. Le temps qu'ils "
"repoussent, nous serons déjà loin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:850
msgid "Let's get to it, then."
msgstr "Bon alors allons-y."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:866
msgid "Hmm, what is this thing?"
msgstr "Hum, qu'est-ce que c'est que ça ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:879
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:396
msgid "Abhai"
msgstr "Abhai"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:885
msgid "EEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!"
msgstr "HIIIIIIIIIIIIIIII !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:890
msgid "AHHHHHHHHH!"
msgstr "AHHHHHHHHH !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:896
msgid "... wait a second, who are you?"
msgstr "... attendez un peu, qui êtes-vous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:901
msgid "I.... I am one of Tallin's men..."
msgstr "Je... je suis l'un des hommes de Tallin..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:906
msgid "Who is this Tallin?"
msgstr "Qui est ce Tallin ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:911
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:28
msgid "I am."
msgstr "C'est moi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:916
msgid "What is your purpose in coming here?"
msgstr "Pourquoi vous êtes-vous aventurés ici ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:921
msgid "We seek the lich Malifor."
msgstr "Nous recherchons Malifor la liche."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:926
msgid ""
"Malifor!... *goes a bit paler (if possible)* What business do you have with "
"him?"
msgstr ""
"Malifor !... *devenant encore un peu plus pâle (si s'est possible)* Pour "
"quelle raison le cherchez-vous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:931
msgid "We seek to crush and destroy him."
msgstr "Nous voulons le réduire en miettes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:936
msgid ""
"Oh, thank the Gods of Light! Finally there is someone here in force to deal "
"with that menace. You must have been sent by the High Kalian of "
"Hiera'Shirsha?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, que les dieux de la lumière soient loués ! Enfin quelqu'un pour "
"s'occuper de cette menace. Vous devez être envoyés par le haut Kalian de "
"Hiera'Shirsha ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:941
msgid "The what!?"
msgstr "Le quoi !?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:946
msgid "Err, I think we might be in different... uh... time zones, here."
msgstr ""
"Euh, je pense qu'il est possible que nous soyons dans des... euh... ''zones "
"temporelles'' différentes ici."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:951
#, fuzzy
msgid "I beg your pardon. Say, what year is it anyway?"
msgstr "Excusez-moi ; dites-moi, en quelle année sommes-nous au fait ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:956
msgid "Uh... 534 YW..."
msgstr "Euh... en 534 YW..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:961
msgid "Huh!? Can't be, the last year I remember it was 14, 318 AD!"
msgstr "Quoi !? Impossible, mes derniers souvenirs remontent à 14 318 AD !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:966
msgid "?????"
msgstr "?????"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:971
msgid "Different calendars, folks."
msgstr "C'est pas les mêmes calendriers, les gars."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:976
msgid "I see, but say, who are you?"
msgstr "Je vois. Mais dites-nous qui vous êtes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:981
msgid "What? How can you not know who I am?"
msgstr "Quoi ? Comment pouvez-vous ne pas savoir qui je suis ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:986
msgid "The times have changed, my friend."
msgstr "Les temps ont changé, l'ami."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:991
msgid ""
"Right... sorry about that. My name is Lord Abhai and I am... or was... the "
"ruler of the great kingdom of Garet-Desh."
msgstr ""
"En effet... c'est bien dommage. Je suis le Seigneur Abhai et je suis... ou "
"plutôt j'étais... le gouverneur du grand royaume de Garet-Desh."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:996
msgid "What happened to you? Why are you a ghost?"
msgstr "Que vous est-il arrivé ? Comment êtes-vous devenu un fantôme ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1001
msgid ""
"I grew old and died as all men do and entered the land of the dead. I don't "
"know how long I dwelled there, I was wrenched from my peace and forced into "
"this ectoplasmic body by a terrible power."
msgstr ""
"Eh bien, avec le temps je suis devenu vieux, puis j'ai fini par mourir comme "
"tout le monde et je suis entré dans le royaume des morts. Je ne sais pas "
"combien de temps j'y suis resté mais, un jour, j'ai été arraché du repos et "
"projeté dans ce corps ectoplasmique par une puissance terrible."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1006
msgid "Let me guess. Malifor?"
msgstr "Laissez-moi deviner, Malifor ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1011
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed. He tried to break my spirit into mindless slavery, but I resisted "
"his power and fled. I have been hiding in these flooded tunnels ever since. "
"Some monster that Malifor's minions greatly fear lives in these waters; they "
"do not molest me here."
msgstr ""
"C'est exact. Il a aussi essayé de me forcer à travailler pour lui comme les "
"autres esclaves sans cervelle, mais j'ai réussi à lui résister et à "
"m'enfuir. Je suis resté caché dans ces galeries inondées depuis lors. Il "
"semblerait qu'un monstre vive dans ces eaux, ce qui explique pourquoi "
"personne ne s'aventure par ici."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1016
msgid "Would you join us to defeat this evil creature?"
msgstr "Vous joindriez-vous à nous pour vaincre cette créature diabolique ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1021
msgid ""
"Wouldn't miss it. Maybe after he is destroyed me and my kind can live... "
"err.... be dead peacefully."
msgstr ""
"Je ne voudrais pas manquer ça. Quand il sera détruit, moi et les miens "
"pourrons peut-être vivre... euh... être morts en paix."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1026
msgid ""
"Keep following these flooded tunnels. I think they might lead you directly "
"to Mailfor."
msgstr ""
"Continuez de suivre ces galeries inondées. Je pense qu'elles pourront vous "
"mener tout droit à Malifor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1031
msgid "Great! Forward, men!"
msgstr "Parfait ! En avant, soldats !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1044
msgid ""
"Just great, I am cold, wet, and tired and what have we here? Another dead "
"end. This place is starting to get on my nerves!"
msgstr ""
"Génial, j'ai froid, je suis trempé et fatigué et qu'avons-nous là ? Encore "
"un cul-de-sac. Cet endroit commence à me taper sur les nerfs !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1057
msgid "Ssssh! I hear something."
msgstr "Chuuut ! J'entends quelque chose."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1060
msgid "Sea Serpent"
msgstr "Serpent de mer"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1064
msgid "ROOOAAARRR!"
msgstr "ROOOAAAHHH !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1069
msgid "Ahhhhh!"
msgstr "Ahhhhh !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1083
msgid "Hold it, people, there is something just ahead!"
msgstr "Attendez les gars, il y a quelque chose qui approche !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1126
msgid " *sniff* I smell humans."
msgstr " *snif* Ça sent l'humain."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1131
msgid "You are just plain deaf. I heard them coming from a mile off."
msgstr ""
"T'es complètement sourd. On les entend venir à un kilomètre à la ronde."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1136
msgid "Ahh, shut up. Let's go kill them."
msgstr "Ahhh, ferme-la et tuons-les."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1150
msgid "A door, and a big, big lock, hmmmmm..."
msgstr "Une porte, avec un très très gros verrou, hmmmmm..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1155
msgid "Sorry folks, this is just too tempting."
msgstr "Désolé les gars, mais c'est vraiment trop tentant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1180
msgid ""
"Hmmmm, this door sure is locked up pretty tight. I wonder what's behind it."
msgstr ""
"Hummm, cette porte est sacrément bien verrouillée. Je me demande ce qu'il y "
"a derrière."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1205
msgid ""
"Holy water! For a certainty, those skeletons won't like us getting our hands "
"on this stuff. But that's probably why they kept them back here in the first "
"place."
msgstr ""
"De l'eau bénite ! Je pense que ces squelettes ne vont pas apprécier que nous "
"mettions la main dessus. Mais c'est certainement pour cette raison qu'ils "
"l'ont gardée ici."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1219
msgid "Oh yeah, holy water!"
msgstr "Ah ouais, de l'eau bénite !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1233
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1255
msgid ""
"Warning! These bottles contain toxic waste. Causes disintegration on contact."
msgstr ""
"Attention ! Ces fioles contiennent un produit toxique. Qui désintègre au "
"contact."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1239
msgid "Ha ha, for skeletons anyway."
msgstr "Ha ha, c'est pour les squelettes de toute façon."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1261
msgid " *rolls eyes* Oh the hazardous life of a skeleton."
msgstr " *roule les yeux* Ah, la dangereuse vie du squelette !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1277
msgid "The Treasury"
msgstr "Le Trésor"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1283
msgid "The Treasury! Cool, let's go loot some booty!"
msgstr "Le trésor ! Cool, allons piller tout ça !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1299
msgid "The Dungeon"
msgstr "Le Donjon"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1316
msgid "Malifor the Great's Study."
msgstr "Étude de Malifor le Grand"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1322
msgid "There we go! This way guys!"
msgstr "C'est par ici ! Allons-y les gars !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1337
msgid "Wow! There is at least 1000 gold in here!"
msgstr "Waouh ! Il y a au moins 1000 pièces d'or là-dedans !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1358
msgid "Holy Gods of Light! 500 gold!"
msgstr "Nom d'un chien ! 500 pièces d'or !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1379
msgid "800 gold! We're rich!!!"
msgstr "800 pièces d'or ! Nous sommes riches !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1400
msgid "What a horde! 2 000 gold!"
msgstr "Y'a une de ces montagnes d'or ! 2000 pièces !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1421
msgid "500 gold! Not bad!"
msgstr "500 pièces d'or ! Pas mal !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1442
msgid "10,000 gold! Wow! Where is that bag of bones getting all this?"
msgstr ""
"10 000 pièces d'or ! Waouh ! Où est-ce que ce sac d'os va trouver tout ça ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:273
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:329
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:382
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:423
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:463
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:522
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:570
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1471
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:416
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:624
msgid "Sister Theta"
msgstr "Sœur Theta"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1484
msgid "Freedom at last. Thank you Lord Tallin."
msgstr "Enfin libre ! Merci, Seigneur Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1489
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Just Tallin. I am no Lord, just a humble peasant trying to restore our "
"people to freedom."
msgstr ""
"Tallin suffira, je ne suis qu'un simple paysan qui essaie de rendre la "
"liberté à son peuple, pas un seigneur."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1501
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1629
msgid "Who are you? How did you end up down here?"
msgstr "Mais qui êtes-vous donc ? Comment avez-vous atterri ici ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1505
msgid ""
"I am called Sister Theta. My husband Marcus and I were advisers and healers "
"for the dwarvish nobles of Knalga. We could not save them from Khazg Black-"
"Tusk's troops, but we survived the orcs and trolls only to be captured when "
"these skeletons appeared."
msgstr ""
"Je m'appelle Sœur Theta. Mon mari Marcus et moi servions de conseillers et "
"de guérisseurs aux nobles nains. Nous n'avons pas pu les sauver des troupes "
"de Khazg Dague-Noire. Nous avons plus ou moins réussi à survivre aux orcs et "
"aux trolls mais, quand ces squelettes apparurent, nous fûmes capturés."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1510
msgid ""
"Funny, why would the bonebag keep you as his prisoners? He didn't seem to be "
"the merciful type."
msgstr ""
"C'est drôle, pourquoi ce sac d'os vous garderait-il prisonniers ? Il ne "
"semble pas spécialement du genre clément."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1515
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"He didn't keep us alive out of mercy, he wanted to study us to see if there "
"was a way to counteract our arcane attacks. His kind are very vulnerable to "
"such attacks, as I am sure you know by now."
msgstr ""
"Il ne nous gardait pas par bonté d'âme, il voulait nous étudier pour trouver "
"un moyen de contrecarrer nos attaques sacrées. Ses semblables sont très "
"sensibles à ce genre d'attaques, comme vous le savez certainement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1520
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1648
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed, that is good to know. But you are now free to go wherever you like. "
"May the Lords of Light guide your path."
msgstr ""
"Oui bien sûr. Mais quoi qu'il en soit, vous êtes désormais libres d'aller où "
"bon vous semble. Puissent les Seigneurs de la Lumière guider vos pas."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1525
msgid ""
"If you have no objection, Tallin, we would like to join you. These "
"northlands are hardly safe these days for anyone to be traveling on their "
"own, and we could lend valuable help to your cause."
msgstr ""
"Si vous n'y voyez pas d'inconvénient, Tallin, nous aimerions nous joindre à "
"vous. Ces Terres du Nord sont plutôt hostiles pour ceux qui voyagent seuls "
"et nous pourrons vous offrir une aide précieuse pour mener votre quête à "
"bien."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1530
msgid "Very well, you are most welcome to join us."
msgstr "Très bien, vous êtes les bienvenus parmi nous."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1535
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1663
msgid "Thank you, Tallin."
msgstr "Merci Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1548
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1676
msgid "Marcus!"
msgstr "Marcus !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1553
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1681
msgid "Theta!"
msgstr "Theta !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1558
msgid "Please folks, not now."
msgstr "S'il vous plaît, pas maintenant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1563
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1691
msgid "Oh, sorry."
msgstr "Oh, pardon."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:628
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:673
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:713
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:757
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:801
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:836
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:880
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1600
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:398
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:606
msgid "Father Marcus"
msgstr "Père Marcus"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1612
msgid ""
"Finally! I am free. Lord Tallin, I am forever in your debt! We will follow "
"you to the end of the World if need be."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, je suis libre ! Seigneur Tallin, j'ai une dette envers vous. Nous "
"vous suivrons jusqu'au bout du monde s'il le faut !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1617
#, fuzzy
msgid "It's just Tallin, no Lord. And no problem."
msgstr "Tallin tout court, pas de seigneur. Et tout le plaisir est pour moi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1633
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am called Father Marcus. My wife, Theta and I were advisers and healers "
"for the dwarvish nobles. We could not shield them from the wrath of Khazg "
"Black-Tusk, but we survived the orcs and trolls -- only to be captured by "
"these skeletons."
msgstr ""
"Je m'appelle Père Marcus. Mon épouse Theta et moi-même servions de "
"conseillers et de guérisseurs aux nobles nains. Nous n'avons pas pu les "
"sauver de la colère de Khazg Dague-Noire. Nous avons plus ou moins réussi à "
"survivre aux orcs et aux trolls mais, quand ces squelettes sont apparus, "
"nous fûmes capturés."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1638
msgid ""
"Funny, why would the bonebag keep you as his prisoners? He doesn't really "
"seem to be the merciful type."
msgstr ""
"C'est drôle, pourquoi ce sac d'os vous garderait-il prisonniers ? Il ne "
"semble pas spécialement du genre clément."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1643
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"He didn't keep us alive out of mercy, he wanted to study us to see if there "
"was a way to counteract our arcane attacks. His kind are very vulnerable to "
"such attacks."
msgstr ""
"Il ne nous gardait pas par bonté d'âme, il voulait nous étudier pour trouver "
"un moyen de contrecarrer nos attaques sacrées. Ses semblables sont très "
"sensibles à ce genre d'attaques, comme vous le savez certainement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1653
msgid ""
"As I have said, Tallin, I am eternally in your debt, and I take my debts "
"seriously. If you have no objection, I will serve you until one of us "
"departs this life."
msgstr ""
"Comme je vous l'ai dit, Tallin, je vous suis éternellement reconnaissant, et "
"je prends mes dettes au sérieux. Si vous n'y voyez pas d'objection, "
"j'aimerais vous servir jusqu'à ce que l'un de nous rencontre la mort."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1658
msgid ""
"Oh, think nothing of it. Let no talk of debts come between us; rather let us "
"join hands as allies in restoring these Northlands to sanity."
msgstr ""
"Oh, pas de ça s'il vous plaît. Ne laissons pas de dettes s'immiscer entre "
"nous et, ensemble, tâchons de nettoyer ces Terres du Nord."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1686
msgid "Please, folks, not now."
msgstr "S'il vous plaît, pas maintenant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1719
msgid ""
"Wow! That's incredible. Now I understand why the Bag of Bones kept you guys "
"in jail; He just simply couldn't kill you!"
msgstr ""
"Waouh ! Incroyable ! Maintenant je comprends VRAIMENT pourquoi le sac d'os "
"vous gardait prisonniers ; il ne pouvait tout bonnement pas vous tuer !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1724
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/09a_Introductions.cfg:243
msgid " *giggle*"
msgstr " *gloussements*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1745
msgid "Elenia"
msgstr "Elenia"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1758
msgid "Oh my, she is almost dead!"
msgstr "Oh mon dieu, elle agonise !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1770
msgid "Here, let me see her."
msgstr "Allez, laissez-moi voir ça."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1785
msgid "Was that a teleport you just did? Wow, you guys are good!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1790
msgid " *wink* *wink*"
msgstr " *sourire facétieux*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1795
msgid "Here, this will help her."
msgstr "Tenez, ça va l'aider."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1804
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1878
msgid "Uh....... where..... am..... I...?"
msgstr "Euh... Où... suis-je ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1809
msgid ""
"You are in the dungeons of Malifor. These brave people have just released "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes dans les cachots de Malifor. Ces braves gens viennent de vous "
"libérer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1814
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1888
msgid "....thanks."
msgstr "... Merci."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1819
msgid ""
"No problem. Sister Theta, you take care of her. If she wants to join us she "
"would make a powerful ally."
msgstr ""
"Aucun problème. Sœur Theta, occupez-vous d'elle. Si elle désire se joindre à "
"nous, elle fera une puissante alliée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1824
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1898
msgid "Yes, I would... like to join... you Lord Tallin."
msgstr "Oui, je voudrais... bien me joindre... à vous... Seigneur Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1829
msgid ""
"Just Tallin; I am no lord. But gee, that sure is some powerful spell you "
"used on her, Sister. She is looking better already."
msgstr ""
"Tallin suffira, je ne suis pas noble. Mais woooh, vous avez dû lui lancer un "
"sort puissant, Sœur Theta, elle semble aller déjà mieux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1834
msgid "And I feel better too. Now let's get back at that disgusting skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Et je me sens mieux également. Maintenant, allons trouver ce squelette "
"dégoûtant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1839
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1917
msgid "Why did the bag of bones capture you in the first place?"
msgstr "Pourquoi ce sac d'os vous a-t-il capturée au fait ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1844
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1922
msgid "Because he thought I was pretty."
msgstr "Parce qu'il me trouvait jolie."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1849
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1927
msgid "That old skeleton? Geez, what a nutcase."
msgstr "Ce vieux squelette ? Il est complètement marteau !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1854
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1932
msgid "You're telling me."
msgstr "Tu m'étonnes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1868
msgid ""
"I wish we had some healers with us. Just try to help her the best you can."
msgstr ""
"Je regrette que nous n'ayons pas de guérisseurs avec nous. Essayez de "
"l'aider du mieux que vous pouvez."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1873
msgid "Here, I hope that helps."
msgstr "Voilà, j'espère que ça aidera."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1883
msgid "You are in the dungeons of Malifor. We have just released you."
msgstr "Vous êtes dans les cachots de Malifor. Nous venons de vous libérer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1893
msgid ""
"No problem. Just take it easy. If you would like to join us your help could "
"mean life or death for a lot of us."
msgstr ""
"Pas de problème. Détendez-vous pour l'instant. Si vous vous joigniez à nous, "
"votre aide serait vitale pour nombre d'entre nous."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1903
msgid "Just Tallin, I am no lord. And you are looking better already."
msgstr "Tallin suffira. Mais vous semblez déjà aller mieux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1912
msgid ""
"Oh, just a few tricks I know, otherwise I probably would be dead by now. But "
"let's get back at that disgusting skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Oh, juste quelques trucs que je connais, sans quoi je serais probablement "
"déjà morte. Enfin bon, occupons-nous plutôt de cet horrible squelette."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:108
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1954
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:593
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:107
msgid "Krash"
msgstr "Krash"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1966
msgid "Holy cow! What did I just let out of that cage! Look out everyone."
msgstr ""
"Nom d'un chien ! Mais qu'est-ce que j'ai libéré ! Regardez tout le monde."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1971
msgid "Oooooh, cool, it's a drake!"
msgstr "Oooooh, cool, un dracan !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1976
msgid " *whimper*"
msgstr " *murmure*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1981
msgid ""
"My God, such a fierce creature whimpering! What the heck have they done to "
"it?"
msgstr ""
"Mon Dieu, voilà une créature aussi féroce qui murmure ! Bon sang, que lui "
"ont-ils donc fait ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1986
msgid "The bastards!"
msgstr "Les enflures !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1991
msgid "Probably another one of Malifor's experiments."
msgstr "Sans doute une autre expérience de Malifor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:1996
msgid "I don't know, see if it talks."
msgstr "Je ne sais pas, regarde si ça peut parler."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2001
msgid "Hey, big guy. We aren't gonna hurt you. We wanna be your friends."
msgstr "Hé, mon grand. On va pas te faire de mal. On veut être tes amis."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2006
msgid ".....not..... going..... to...... hurt.... me?"
msgstr "pas... faire... mal... à moi ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2011
msgid "Hey, it talks!"
msgstr "Hé, ça parle !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2016
#, fuzzy
msgid "It's a 'he', and yes, they're actually very intelligent creatures."
msgstr ""
"Oui, « il » parle et oui, ce sont vraiment des créatures très intelligentes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2021
msgid ""
"Hush! I am trying to talk to him. Nope, we'll never hurt you. But if you "
"want to you can hurt some skeletons."
msgstr ""
"Chut, j'essaie de lui parler. Nan, on ne te fera jamais de mal. Mais si tu "
"veux, tu peux faire mal aux squelettes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2026
msgid "Skeletons! GRRRRRRRR!!!"
msgstr "Squelettes ! GRRRRRRRR !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2031
msgid "Look out! He is ready to go! Hey, is that smoke coming out of his ears?"
msgstr ""
"Regardez ! Il est prêt à y aller ! Hé, c'est bien de la fumée qui sort de "
"ses oreilles ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2036
msgid ""
"And look at this, there is some sort of opening in the back of his cell..."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2041
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It's an escape tunnel. The hole wasn't big enough for me to go through but "
"one you little guys you might fit."
msgstr ""
"Hé, il y a un passage juste derrière cette cellule. Le trou n'était pas "
"assez grand pour que je puisse y passer mais peut-être que l'un de vous "
"pourra s'y faufiler."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2046
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hmmm, it is pretty small, let's see if we can make it bigger."
msgstr ""
"Ouais, t'as raison. Humm, c'est vrai que c'est pas grand. Voyons voir si je "
"peux arranger ça."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2057
msgid "There we go. Now let's see where this tunnel leads to."
msgstr "Nous y voilà. Voyons maintenant sur quoi cela débouche."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2069
msgid "ROOOOOOAAAARRRR!"
msgstr "ROOOOOOAAAAHHHH !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2074
msgid ""
"Woha! Maybe he isn't so friendly after all... or at least to some things."
msgstr ""
"Ouaah ! Il n'est peut-être pas si gentil que ça, tout compte fait... enfin, "
"ça dépend avec qui."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2091
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA, FOOLS, YOU THINK YOU CAN KILL ME?"
msgstr "HAHAHAHA, PAUVRES FOUS, VOUS CROYEZ POUVOIR ME TUER ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2140
msgid "What the...!"
msgstr "C'est quoi ce délire !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2145
msgid "How can it be?! Our axes and hammers are failing."
msgstr "Comment est-ce possible ? Nos marteaux et nos haches sont inefficaces."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2150
msgid "Blast it! Now where did he go? Let's find him and try something else!"
msgstr ""
"Malédiction ! Mais où est-il passé ? Trouvons-le et essayons autre chose !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2155
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2261
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2367
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2468
msgid "I see now. It is impossible to destroy him by ordinary means."
msgstr "Je vois. On ne peut pas le détruire par des moyens ordinaires."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2160
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2266
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2372
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2473
msgid "Then how are we going to destroy him? Surely there must be a way."
msgstr "Alors comment allons-nous faire ? Il doit bien y avoir un moyen."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2165
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2271
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2377
msgid ""
"Yes, I think there is, but only myself or Theta have the means to do it. "
"Come on Theta, let's destroy that old skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Oui, je pense aussi, mais seuls Theta et moi avons de quoi le détruire. "
"Viens, Theta, allons détruire ce vieux squelette."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2170
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2276
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2382
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2483
msgid "Yeah, I can't wait to get my hands on that bastard!"
msgstr "Ouais, je suis impatiente de choper cet enfoiré !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2175
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2281
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2387
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2488
msgid "That was very unladylike of you."
msgstr "Ce langage n'est guère convenable pour une dame comme vous."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:592
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2180
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2286
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2392
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2493
msgid " *giggle* Sorry."
msgstr " *gloussements* Désolée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2197
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, YOUR IDIOCY AMUSES ME GREATLY!"
msgstr "HAHAHAHAHAHA, VOTRE STUPIDITÉ M'AMUSE GRANDEMENT !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2221
msgid "COME AND GET ME!"
msgstr "VENEZ ME CHERCHER !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2226
msgid "Geez, how are we going to kill him?"
msgstr "Mince, comment allons-nous le tuer ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2231
msgid "Well, obviously clubs and arrows won't work."
msgstr "Eh bien, les massues et les flèches n'auront assurément aucun effet."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2236
msgid "Oh darn, he disappeared. Let's find him and try a different weapon."
msgstr ""
"Ah malédiction, il a disparu ! Retrouvons-le et essayons une arme différente."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2303
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, DEATH HAS NO EFFECT ON ME YOU FOOLS!"
msgstr "HAHAHAHAHAHA, LA MORT N'A PAS D'EFFET SUR MOI, BANDE D'IDIOTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2327
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA, I CAN NEVER BE DESTROYED!"
msgstr "HAHAHAHAHA, JE SUIS INVULNÉRABLE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2332
msgid "Oh yes you will! But... how?"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2337
msgid "Well, it sure isn't gonna be done with a blade."
msgstr "Bon, c'est sûr qu'on va pas réussir avec une épée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2342
msgid "And look, he's gone. Now we gotta find him all over again!"
msgstr "Et regardez, il s'est envolé. On va encore devoir le retrouver !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2409
msgid "HAHAHAHAHAHA, I AM IMMORTAL!"
msgstr "HAHAHAHAHAHA, JE SUIS IMMORTEL !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2453
msgid "YOU PUNY MORTALS SHALL SOON BE SERVING ME!"
msgstr "VOUS RAMPEREZ BIENTÔT À MES PIEDS, FAIBLES MORTELS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2458
msgid "That blasted skeleton! Even fire has no affect on him!"
msgstr "Ce maudit squelette ! Même le feu reste sans effet !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2463
msgid ""
"Look, he disappeared again. Let's find him and try using a different weapon "
"on him."
msgstr ""
"Regardez, il a encore disparu. Trouvons-le et essayons une arme différente."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2478
msgid ""
"Yes, I think there is, but only myself or Theta have the means to do it. "
"Come on, Theta, let's destroy that old skeleton."
msgstr ""
"Oui, je pense aussi, mais seuls Theta et moi avons de quoi le détruire. "
"Viens, Theta, allons détruire ce vieux squelette."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2509
msgid "AHHHHHH! YOU BLASTED MAGE!"
msgstr "AHHHHHH ! MAUDIT MAGE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2514
msgid "Good. We finally got him. He is just dissolving."
msgstr "Bien. On l'a eu pour finir. Il se dissout littéralement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2519
msgid ""
"Curses on you you blasted mages, curses on you you blasted dwarves, curses "
"on you you blasted humans, and CURSES ON YOU YOU BLASTED TALLIN! MAY YOUR "
"MISERABLE LIVES BE FULL OF TORTURE! MAY YOUR PEOPLE NEVER BE FREE! MAY ALL "
"YOUR NEAR AND DEAR DESERT YOU! MAY A THUNDERBOLT HIT YOUR HEAD! MAY..."
msgstr ""
"Soyez maudits, mages ! Soyez maudits, nains ! Soyez maudits, humains ! Et "
"SOIS MAUDIT, TALLIN ! QUE VOS MISÉRABLES VIES NE SOIENT PLUS QU'UNE LONGUE "
"TORTURE ! QUE VOS GENS NE SOIENT JAMAIS LIBRES ! QUE VOS CHERS ET TENDRES "
"VOUS ABANDONNENT ! QUE LA FOUDRE FRAPPE VOS TÊTES ! QUE..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2524
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:459
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:668
msgid "May you shut your ugly mouth and hurry up and die."
msgstr "Que tu fermes ta sale gueule et que tu meures en vitesse."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2529
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:464
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:673
msgid ""
"MAY THE EARTH OPEN UP AND SWALLOW YOU! MAY ALL YOUR TEETH FALL OUT! MAY YOU "
"BECOME A WEAK SKINNY OLD MAN! MAY............."
msgstr ""
"QUE LA TERRE S'OUVRE ET VOUS ENGLOUTISSE ! QUE VOS DENTS TOMBENT ! QUE VOTRE "
"CHAIR VIEILLISE ET PÉRISSE ! QUE........"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2534
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:474
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:683
msgid "Finally! He has been reduced to dust."
msgstr "Enfin ! Ce n'est plus qu'un amas de poussière."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2539
#, fuzzy
msgid "At last! Victory is ours! Good work, men!"
msgstr "Enfin ! La victoire est à nous ! Bon boulot, les gars !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2544
#, fuzzy
msgid "So, where to now, Tallin?"
msgstr "Où allons-nous maintenant, Tallin ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2549
msgid ""
"Now, let's get back to the dwarves and see what progress they have made in "
"forging us weapons."
msgstr ""
"Retournons chez les nains et voyons comment ils se débrouillent avec ces "
"nouvelles armes qu'ils nous forgent."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2569
msgid "They are trying to free the prisoners! Stop them!"
msgstr "Ils tentent de libérer les prisonniers ! Arrêtez-les !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2574
msgid "Good luck, my friend."
msgstr "Bonne chance, l'ami."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2622
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3038
msgid "Intruders! Get them!"
msgstr "Des intrus ! Attrapez-les !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2627
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3043
msgid "Bring it on!"
msgstr "Venez me chercher !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2695
msgid ""
"They are attacking the master's study! We must stop them! Call the reserves!"
msgstr ""
"Ils attaquent l'étude du maître ! Nous devons les arrêter ! Ramenez des "
"renforts !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2700
msgid " 'The master's study' eh? I bet we'll find Mailfor there!"
msgstr "« L'étude du maître », hein ? Je parie que nous y trouverons Malifor !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2764
msgid "Ugh, a dead body!"
msgstr "Beurk, un cadavre !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2781
msgid "Here's another body."
msgstr "En voici un autre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2798
msgid "And another..."
msgstr "Et encore un autre..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2815
msgid ""
"Gee, what's with all these bodies floating around? Is this river some sort "
"of body disposal?"
msgstr ""
"Bon dieu, qu'est-ce que c'est que tous ces corps qui flottent ? C'est une "
"espèce de fosse commune, cette rivière ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2832
msgid "The Great Chamber"
msgstr "La Chambre Colossale"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2838
msgid " 'The Great Chamber'? Hmmm, wonder what that could be."
msgstr ""
"« La Chambre Colossale » ? Hemm, je m'demande ce que ça peut bien être."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2855
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So this is the Great Chamber eh? Doesn't look like there is much to see here."
msgstr ""
"Alors c'est ça la Chambre Colossale, hein ? On dirait qu'y a pas grand-chose "
"à voir ici."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2862
msgid " *rumble*"
msgstr " *grondement*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2868
#, fuzzy
msgid "Perhaps I spoke too soon..."
msgstr "Oups, j'ai parlé trop vite."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2876
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2978
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3261
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3427
msgid " *CRASH*"
msgstr " *CRACK*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2882
#, fuzzy
msgid "What was that? Oh, woe - two big slabs of rock cutting off our retreat!"
msgstr ""
"Qu'est-ce que c'était ? Oh mer... deux énormes pierres bloquent l'issue !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2990
msgid "Hsssssssss"
msgstr "Tsssssssss"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:2995
msgid "This doesn't look good."
msgstr "C'est pas bon signe."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3001
#, fuzzy
msgid "Great Chamber my foot! This is a Death Chamber!"
msgstr "Chambre Colossale, mon œil ! Ça devrait s'appeler « Chambre Macabre »."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3021
msgid "Here we go."
msgstr "Voilà."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3121
msgid "Dulcatas"
msgstr "Dulcatas"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3134
msgid "Antolos"
msgstr "Antolos"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3147
msgid "Varem"
msgstr "Varem"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3159
msgid "Halt! Who goes there? Friend or foe?"
msgstr "Halte ! Qui va là ? Ami ou ennemi ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3164
msgid "Depends. Are you loyal to Malifor?"
msgstr "Ça dépend. Êtes-vous des serviteurs de Malifor ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3169
msgid ""
"Never! If you ha' been sent by Malifor, then know that we will never yield! "
"Come and meet your death!"
msgstr ""
"Jamais ! Si Malifor vous envoie, sachez que nous n'abandonnerons jamais ! En "
"garde !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3174
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hold! We aren't friends of Malifor in the least. Rather, we have come to "
"destroy him."
msgstr ""
"Attendez un peu, nous ne sommes pas le moins du monde des amis de Malifor, "
"au contraire nous venons pour l'anéantir."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3179
msgid "Finally! You don't know how long we have been waiting for this day."
msgstr ""
"Enfin ! Vous n'imaginez pas combien de temps nous avons attendu ce jour."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3184
msgid "How did you get here and how long have you been here?"
msgstr "Quand et comment êtes-vous arrivés ici ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3189
msgid ""
"We were originally prisoners of Malifor, but we tunnelled out and escaped. "
"Since then, we have eked out a precarious survival on what we have been able "
"to steal or raid from Malifor."
msgstr ""
"Nous étions d'abord des prisonniers de Malifor, mais nous avons réussi à "
"creuser un passage et nous nous sommes enfuis. Depuis, nous réussissons à "
"peine à survivre en lui volant ce que nous pouvons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3194
msgid "By now you have tunnels all through this place."
msgstr "Je parie que maintenant vous avez des galeries un peu partout."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3199
msgid ""
"Aye. That seemingly blank wall to the south there is actually a hidden "
"entrance to the treasury."
msgstr ""
"C'est exact. Par exemple, au sud, ce mur d'allure parfaitement innocente est "
"en fait un passage secret vers le trésor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3204
msgid "Awesome, let's go!"
msgstr "Génial, allons-y !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3219
msgid ""
" *sigh* Great. More water. And there doesn't seem to be anything down this "
"tunnel, either friend or foe."
msgstr ""
"Pfffff. Super. Encore de l'eau. Et il n'y a même pas l'air d'y avoir quelque "
"chose au bout de ce tunnel, ami ou ennemi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3244
msgid "Hmmm, another door. Boy, is this one sure locked up."
msgstr "Humm, encore une porte. Celle-là est verrouillée, et bien verrouillée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3249
msgid "Anything you can't handle?"
msgstr "Tu peux t'en charger ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3254
msgid "Nope. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Ouaip. Je l'ouvre ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3257
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3596
msgid "Go for it!"
msgstr "C'est parti !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:641
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3276
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3442
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3657
msgid "There we go."
msgstr "Voilà."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3300
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3464
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3680
msgid "You wretched vermin, I have had it with you! Guards!"
msgstr "Sale petite vermine, j'en ai plus qu'assez de te voir ! Gardes !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3390
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3552
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3771
msgid "Just wait a sec."
msgstr "Attends une minute."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3420
msgid ""
"It looks like this is it. Here is the door to Malifor's study. Are we all "
"ready for this?"
msgstr ""
"Apparemment, on y est, les gars ; voici la porte d'entrée de l'étude de "
"Malifor. Est-ce qu'on est fin prêts pour ce qui nous y attend ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3423
msgid "Yeah, open those doors!"
msgstr "Ouais, ouvre-moi ces portes !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3583
msgid "Hey, check this out, it looks like some sort of lever."
msgstr "Hé, regardez ça, on dirait une sorte de levier."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3588
msgid "Probably for that door right there."
msgstr "Il sert sûrement à ouvrir la porte qui est là."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3593
msgid "Should I throw it?"
msgstr "Je peux le tirer ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3601
msgid "Ok, here we go!"
msgstr "Bien, c'est parti !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3606
msgid " *creak*....."
msgstr " *criiic*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3611
msgid "Nothing. That door is not moving."
msgstr "Rien... La porte n'a pas bougé d'un poil."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3616
msgid "Why don't you try 'knocking'."
msgstr "Pourquoi ne pas « frapper » ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3621
msgid "Ok."
msgstr "D'accord."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3626
msgid " *BANG*"
msgstr " *BANG*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3631
msgid "Anybody home?"
msgstr "Y'a quelqu'un ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3636
msgid " *BOOM*"
msgstr " *BOUM*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05a_The_Pursuit.cfg:3641
msgid " *CRASH!!!*"
msgstr " *CRAAAACK !*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:4
msgid "Compelled"
msgstr "Contraint"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:9
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note: The work on this branch of the campaign is in progress."
msgstr ""
"Remarque : le travail sur cette branche de la campagne est en cours. Il sera "
"fini pour la version 2.0."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:13
msgid ""
"Thus, compelled by some strange and irresistible force, Tallin - eyes glazed "
"and mind unthinking - did the will of his new master."
msgstr ""
"C'est ainsi que, mu par une force étrange et irrésistible, Tallin - les yeux "
"vitreux et l'esprit ailleurs - réalisait la volonté de son nouveau maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"He was first stripped of his weapons and armor and then cast into solitary "
"confinement. He remained there for months, never being allowed to see the "
"light of day, being fed only enough food to keep him alive. During this time "
"he was forced to study the most dark and forbidden arts, lashed with whips "
"when he could not recite lessons drawn from grimoires no human should ever "
"have opened. His body grew feeble and emaciated and his mind plunged ever "
"deeper into night. And day by day the magical controls Malifor had fastened "
"about Tallin's will grew stronger."
msgstr ""
"On lui enleva d'abord ses armes et son armure. Il fut ensuite enfermé dans "
"un solide cachot. Il y resta pendant des mois, sans voir la lumière du jour, "
"nourri avec juste ce qu'il faut pour rester en vie. Pendant tout ce temps, "
"on le força à étudier les arts les plus noirs et les plus interdits. Son "
"corps s'affaiblissait et s'amaigrissait. Son esprit s'enfonça encore plus "
"profondément dans la nuit. Et jour après jour, l'influence magique que "
"Malifor avait construit autour de la volonté de Tallin se renforçait."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Tallin never knew exactly how much time passed, but eventually Malifor's "
"lich-servants declared him fit for service and he was summoned before their "
"dread Master. Through a hideous blood ritual, Malifor gave him the power to "
"animate corpses. He was then sent to a distant network of tunnels to clear "
"out a group of trolls who had taken up residence there."
msgstr ""
"Tallin ne sut jamais combien de temps exactement passa, mais les serviteurs "
"de Malifor finirent par le déclarer bon pour le service, et il fut appelé "
"par leur horrible maître. Grâce à un affreux rituel de sang, Malifor lui "
"donna le pouvoir de réanimer les corps. Il fut ensuite envoyé dans un "
"lointain réseau de galeries pour anéantir un groupe de trolls qui y avaient "
"élu domicile."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:40
msgid "Kill the Troll Leaders"
msgstr "Vaincre les chefs trolls"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:185
msgid "Franik"
msgstr "Franik"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:199
msgid "Henie"
msgstr "Henie"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/05b_Compelled.cfg:241
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:331
msgid "Argh! I have failed my master."
msgstr "Non ! Maître, j'ai échoué."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:24
msgid "Old Friend"
msgstr "Vieil ami"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:30
msgid ""
"Laden with gold, and filled with an elation at their victory that was "
"tempered with sadness at the death of their friends, Tallin and his people "
"made their way back to the mines."
msgstr ""
"Chargés d'or et remplis de joie suite à leur victoire, mais aussi accablés "
"par la tristesse causée par la perte de leurs amis, Tallin et ses hommes "
"reprirent le chemin des mines."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:34
msgid ""
"As they approached they were met with a most welcome sight: New "
"fortifications, looking very much like the legendary impenetrable dwarvish "
"defenses of old, had sprung up everywhere. All of them were manned by alert "
"and well-armed dwarves who hailed them boisterously. The mines were belching "
"smoke from the furiously working forges. New weapons and armor for humans "
"and dwarves alike lay neatly stacked, and the deafening clang of hammers and "
"picks from the dwarves promised more."
msgstr ""
"Le spectacle qu'ils virent en arrivant les ravit : il y avait partout de "
"nouvelles défenses, fort semblables aux légendaires et imprenables "
"fortifications naines de jadis. Elles étaient gardées par des nains alertes "
"et bien armés qui les acclamèrent bruyamment. Les mines crachaient la fumée "
"des forges où il y avait une activité furieuse pour fabriquer de nouvelles "
"armes et de nouvelles armures pour les humains et pour les nains, et le choc "
"assourdissant des marteaux des forgerons nains et des pioches des mineurs en "
"annonçait encore d'autres."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:38
msgid ""
"They found Hamel in a forge hammering away at a new axe. He greeted them "
"warmly and arrangements were quickly made for all their food and "
"accommodations, as wall as care for the sick and wounded."
msgstr ""
"Ils trouvèrent Hamel en train de forger une nouvelle hache. Il les salua "
"chaleureusement et des dispositions furent rapidement prises pour le manger "
"et le coucher, et pour qu'on s'occupe des malades et des blessés."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:42
msgid ""
"When Tallin's party had shaken the dust of the road from their clothes, the "
"humans and dwarves once again met in council."
msgstr ""
"Quand les hommes de Tallin eurent débarrassé leurs vêtements de la poussière "
"du voyage, les humains et les nains tinrent un nouveau conseil."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:46
msgid "It is well, Hamel. You our people prosper."
msgstr "Merci, Hamel. Puissent nos peuples prospérer à nouveau."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:51
msgid ""
"Aye. Word ha' spread, and dwarves who had been living rough in the wilds for "
"fear of the orcs have been coming to join us. Thanks to you, Tallin, Knalga "
"is rising again!"
msgstr ""
"Ouais. Notre réputation grandit, et les nains qui vivaient à la surface, "
"craignant les orcs, sont venus nous rejoindre. Grâce à toi, Tallin, Knalga "
"se relève !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:56
msgid ""
"We have cleared the connecting tunnels to here and to the old keep as well "
"as other parts o' Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons nettoyé les galeries reliant ce fort à l'ancien, ainsi que "
"d'autres parties de Knalga."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:61
msgid ""
"It is slow and dangerous work, mostly due to the trolls. But it ha' been "
"made easier by Malifor's ending."
msgstr ""
"C'est lent, c'est dangereux, surtout à cause des trolls. Mais c'est plus "
"facile depuis la mort de Malifor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:66
msgid ""
"The lich's skeletons were fighting the trolls, but when you destroyed him, "
"they all just fell apart. So, there are many tunnels that are now infested "
"with nothing but piles of old bones."
msgstr ""
"Les squelettes de la liche se battaient contre les trolls, mais se sont "
"simplement désagrégés quand vous avez détruit Malifor. Beaucoup de tunnels "
"ne sont donc plus remplis que par des vieux tas d'os."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:71
msgid "Great! How about the weapons and armor?"
msgstr "Super ! Qu'en est-il des armes et des armures ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:76
msgid ""
"As you can see, Tallin, there are muckle heaps of them, all ready to be "
"borne into battle."
msgstr ""
"Comme tu peux voir, Tallin, il y en a des piles complètes, toutes prêtes à "
"servir au combat."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:81
msgid ""
"What's more, some of the dwarves who are expert with the sword, mace and "
"bow, as well as some of yer own men who have grown skilled by experience, "
"can teach others how to wield them."
msgstr ""
"Et puis certains nains experts à l'épée, à la masse ou à l'arc, ou certains "
"de tes vétérans, pourront entraîner les autres au maniement des armes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:86
msgid ""
"I didn't know that you dwarves knew swordplay. I thought you all fought with "
"axes, hammers or those thunder weapons."
msgstr ""
"Tiens, j'ignorais que les nains savaient manier l'épée. Je pensais que vous "
"vous battiez tous à la hache, au marteau ou avec ces bâtons de tonnerre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:91
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Aye, it's true we do prefer our axes and hammers, but then again, we make "
"swords. We couldna' claim to be expert weaponsmiths wi'out kenning how to "
"wield the weapons we make."
msgstr ""
"Oui, c'est vrai que nous préférons nos haches et nos marteaux mais, encore "
"une fois, nous forgeons des épées. Nous devons savoir manier les armes que "
"nous créons pour pouvoir nous proclamer maîtres-forgerons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:96
msgid ""
"There are some dwarves out there that are bonny fighters wi' a sword as any "
"ye are like to meet. Belike with bows, maces and any other weapons we "
"fashion."
msgstr ""
"Crois-moi, il y a ici de super combattant nains, redoutables à l'épée, ou à "
"l'arc, ou encore à la masse. Ou toute autre arme que nous fabriquons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:101
msgid ""
"That's great! What is the price of your weapons? We have gathered much booty "
"from Malifor's treasury and we will be able to pay you generously."
msgstr ""
"Parfait ! Alors quel est le prix de ces armes ? Nous avons dégoté un gros "
"magot dans la trésorerie de Malifor et je suis sûr que nous pourrons vous "
"payer grassement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:106
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Price?!? Don't insult us, Tallin. Ye have done great things to help the "
"dwarves - it's because of you that we ha' made a start rebuilding Knalga in "
"the first place. Dinna ye speak of price to us."
msgstr ""
"Uu prix !?! Ne nous insulte pas, Tallin. T'as fait tellement de choses pour "
"nous : c'est grâce à vous, et à vous seuls, que nous avons pu r'commencer la "
"reconstruction de Knalga. Alors ne parlons pas pognon."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:111
msgid "But don't you need the gold to help rebuild Knalga? And we have plenty."
msgstr ""
"Mais vous avez bien besoin de cet or pour reconstruire Knalga, n'est-ce "
"pas ? Et puis, on en a plein."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:116
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Tallin, Knalga was an extremely rich nation. Malifor's treasury is hardly a "
"fraction of the riches that we will find, and are finding every day now. So "
"nae! Ye'll need yon gold to rebuild Dwarven Doors."
msgstr ""
"Tallin, Knalga était une nation très très riche. Le trésor de Malifor est à "
"peine une fraction des richesses que nous trouverons, et que nous trouvons à "
"chaque nouvelle journée. Alors, non, que dalle, merci ! Et puis, t'en auras "
"besoin, de ton or, pour reconstruire les Portes des Nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:121
msgid "Thank you, Hamel."
msgstr "Merci, Hamel."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:126
msgid "Pahhh, thank YOU!"
msgstr "Pfff, merci à TOI !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:131
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And Tallin, one more thing, I have been leading our people into battle for "
"many years now. As a young dwarf I was trained in the arts of leadership and "
"war. There are things you will need to know..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, Tallin, autre chose... J'ai mené mon peuple à la bataille pendant de "
"nombreuses années maintenant. Quand je n'étais qu'un jeune nain, j'ai été "
"entraîné dans les arts de la guerre et du commandement. Y'a certaines choses "
"que tu vas devoir apprendre ... "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:136
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know you're impressive wi' a pitchfork, and you are not half bad with a "
"sword when you choose to use one. But there skills beyond swingin' a weapon "
"that a general must learn."
msgstr ""
"Je sais que t'es très impressionnant avec une fourche, et que tu te démerdes "
"bien avec une épée quand tu t'en sers. Mais y'a d'autres trucs que le "
"maniement des armes qu'un général se doit de connaitre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:141
msgid "I would be honored, Lord Hamel."
msgstr "J'en serais honoré, Seigneur Hamel."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:146
msgid ""
"Ahhhh, quit with the formality, me lad. Now, first things first. One of the "
"most important things about being a leader is...."
msgstr ""
"Ahhhh, arrête un peu avec toutes ces politesses. Commençons par le "
"commencement : la chose la plus importante pour un chef, c'est..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:151
msgid ""
"The humans rested for many days while they were equipped with new arms and "
"armor and trained by the dwarves."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi, les humains se reposèrent plusieurs jours, s'équipèrent de nouvelles "
"armes et d'armures neuves, et s'entraînèrent avec les nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:155
msgid ""
"But the peace was not to last. Early one morning Tallin (sore from head to "
"foot from his training) was startled awake by the blare of trumpets, the "
"pounding of drums and the clash of steel as the humans and dwarves hurried "
"to arm themselves."
msgstr ""
"Cependant, la paix ne dura pas. Un matin de bonne heure, Tallin (meurtri des "
"pieds à la tête à cause de son entraînement) fut arraché du sommeil par le "
"son des trompettes, les battements des tambours et le choc des épées alors "
"que les humains et les nains se hâtaient de s'armer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:159
msgid ""
"He sought out Hamel, who informed him that a massive host of orcs had "
"arrived at the gates of the new Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Il alla vite chercher Hamel qui l'informa que toute une armée d'orcs était "
"aux portes de Knalga."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:163
msgid ""
"It was decided that Tallin's men sould sally forth to meet the orcs, while "
"Hamel's held open their retreat into the caves."
msgstr ""
"Il fut décidé que les hommes de Tallin sortent à la rencontre des orcs, "
"tandis que ceux d'Hamel maintiendraient ouverte leur retraite dans les "
"cavernes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:210
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:313
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:59
msgid "Rakshas"
msgstr "Rakshas"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:330
msgid "Drung"
msgstr "Drung"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:347
msgid "Poul"
msgstr "Poul"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:450
msgid "So I see you fat pigs finally mustered up the courage to face me."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:455
msgid "Who are you, what do you want?"
msgstr "Qui êtes-vous et que voulez-vous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:460
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am Emperor Rakshas and by the power of my sword, I lead the orcish people. "
"I am here simply finishing the job Khazg Black - Tusk started years ago - "
"the conquest of Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Je suis l'Empereur Rakshas, chef du peuple orc. Ma mission est d'unir le "
"peuple orc et de finir le travail que nous avons commencé il y a des années."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:465
msgid ""
"Khazg tried and failed, and if you repeat his folly you will soon join him "
"in the land of the dead!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:470
msgid ""
"Pah! I would like to see those cowardly dwarves try their treachery on me as "
"they did on The Black - Tusk! In any case, those dwarves will soon be "
"groveling at my feet and equipping my people with the finest weapons. With "
"the dwarvish weapons, and the wealth of Knalga, nothing will be able to stop "
"us. Even that little backwater that you humans call Wesnoth will be nothing "
"but a burnt out, pillaged wreck before long."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:475
msgid "Boy, this guy sure has delusions of grandeur."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:480
msgid ""
"I am not so sure it's that simple Tallin. Think back to those orcs back in "
"dwarven doors, and those wolves on the way to the mines; they were both "
"saying something about 'The Master'."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:485
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr "Ouais ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:490
msgid "Well, unless I miss my guess, dreamy fellow would be him."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:495
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well, if that is so, then it's time to end this menace once and for all! "
"Fall on them boys!"
msgstr ""
"Mouais, c'est bien lui. Eh bien, soldats, il est temps d'éradiquer cette "
"menace une bonne fois pour toutes ! POUR LES PORTES DES NAINS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:501
msgid "Defeat Rakshas... if you can..."
msgstr "Tuez Rakshas... si vous le pouvez..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:505
msgid "Or, resist till end of turns"
msgstr "Ou, résistez jusqu'à la fin des tours"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:523
msgid "Ahhhh! Run for your life!"
msgstr "Ahhhh ! Sauve qui peut !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:528
msgid "What the... Hey, where do you think you are running off to you coward!"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que ... Hé, où est-ce que tu vas, poule mouillée ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:533
msgid "Stop him!"
msgstr "Arrêtez-le !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:538
msgid ""
"It's too late, I am sorry, Tallin, he got away! We did not expect he would "
"flee like a coward."
msgstr ""
"C'est trop tard, je suis désolé, Tallin, il est parti ! Nous n'avions pas "
"prévu qu'il s'enfuirait comme un trouillard."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Damn! We had the opportunity to end the war in one stroke there. Now we will "
"have to go after him, assuming we can break this siege!"
msgstr ""
"Sacrebleu ! Nous pouvions terminer cette guerre par cette seule attaque. "
"Maintenant, nous allons devoir nous lancer à sa poursuite, en supposant que "
"l'on puisse mettre fin à ce siège !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:551
msgid ""
"Geez, we have been fighting them for three whole days and nights now with no "
"end in sight. Now the forth night is approaching, what should we do?"
msgstr ""
"Purée ! Cela fait maintenant trois jours et trois nuits que nous combattons "
"les orcs et nous n'en voyons toujours pas le bout. La quatrième nuit "
"approche, que devons-nous faire ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:556
msgid ""
"It seems hopeless to continue on like this. The orcs numbers are unlimited "
"and Rakshas is very well guarded. The only possible outcome to all this is "
"more slaughter."
msgstr ""
"Il est inutile de continuer ainsi. Les orcs sont en nombre illimité et "
"Rakshas est trop bien gardé. Tout ceci ne peut finir qu'en carnage."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:561
msgid ""
"I propose that we retreat back into the caves and consult with the dwarves."
msgstr ""
"Je propose de battre en retraite dans les cavernes et de consulter les nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:568
msgid "I agree, Tallin, it is pointless to cary on."
msgstr ""
"Je suis d'accord avec toi, Tallin. Ça ne servirait à rien de continuer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:573
msgid "Very well. Everyone fall back!"
msgstr "Très bien. Que tout le monde se replie !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:578
msgid "Awwwww! Just when I was having the most fun!"
msgstr "Oohhh, je commençais seulement à m'amuser !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:597
msgid ""
"So your forces are managing to advance upon me are they? Very impressive but "
"it shall do you no good. KNIGHTS!!!"
msgstr ""
"Alors tes forces arrivent à gagner du terrain contre moi ? Très "
"impressionnant, mais ça ne te servira à rien. CHEVALIERS !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:656
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA, GOT YOU, SUCKERS!"
msgstr "HA HA HA HA HA. JE VOUS AI BIEN EUS, ORDURES !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:661
msgid "CHARGE!!!"
msgstr "CHARGEZ !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:666
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, hell! Form up men, back to back, don't let them penetrate our ranks."
msgstr ""
"Enfer et damnation ! Formez les rangs, dos à dos, ne les laissez pas percer "
"nos défenses."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:671
msgid "That's not all, my friends. GENERALS, CALL THE RESERVES!"
msgstr "Ce n'est pas tout, chers amis. GENERAUX, ENVOYEZ LES RENFORTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:676
msgid "Oh yeah!"
msgstr "Ah ouais !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:681
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:406
msgid "HAHAHAHAHA!"
msgstr "HA HA HA HA HA !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:686
msgid "Oooooooh! Time to start the fun!"
msgstr "Ooooooh ! On va commencer à rigoler !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:691
msgid "You are so dead, you human vermin!"
msgstr "Vous êtes déjà morts, pourritures d'humains !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:717
msgid "This doesn't look good..."
msgstr "Ça n'a pas l'air bon du tout..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:729
msgid "Argh! I have been slain!"
msgstr "Argh ! Je meurs !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Killed him! Got his gold too. Lets see, hmmmmm, about 500 gold pieces. Not "
"bad."
msgstr ""
"On l'a eu ! Et son or aussi. Voyons voir... hmmmmm environ 500 pièces d'or. "
"Pas mal."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:744
msgid "They have killed one of my generals! REINFORCEMENTS!"
msgstr "Ils ont tué un de mes généraux ! RENFORTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:781
msgid ""
"My death will only make the Master's punishment for you worse you fools!"
msgstr ""
"Ma mort ne rendra le châtiment du maître que plus terrible, bande "
"d'imbéciles !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:786
msgid "Your death makes your Master's punishment from us one step closer!"
msgstr "Ta mort ne fait que rapprocher la punition de ton maître !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:791
#, fuzzy
msgid "But my my, what's in that big pouch? 300 gold! Not bad."
msgstr ""
"Mais tiens tiens, qu'y a-t-il dans cette grosse bourse ? 300 pièces d'or ! "
"Pas mal."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:801
msgid "You vermin will pay for that! REINFORCEMENTS!"
msgstr "Vous paierez pour cet affront, vermines ! DES RENFORTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:838
msgid "Ahhhh! The defilers have slain me!"
msgstr "Ahhhh ! Ces saletés m'ont tué !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:843
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Geez, you sound like some sort of religious fanatic! Let's see what's in the "
"collection plate..."
msgstr ""
"C'est dingue, on croirait entendre une espèce de fanatique religieux ! Eh "
"bien, voyons voir ce qu'il a sous la jupe..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:848
msgid "Ahhh, yes, 400 gold. Praise the Master *snicker* ."
msgstr "Ahhh oui, 400 pièces d'or. Loué soit le maître *ricanements*."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:858
msgid ""
"What! My loyal Flang is gone! You human worms shall pay! REINFORCEMENTS!"
msgstr ""
"Quoi ! Mon fidèle Flang est tombé ! Vous le paierez, vermines d'humains ! JE "
"VEUX DES RENFORTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:895
msgid ""
"What! I die! But how can this be? The master told me that I would always be "
"one of his generals."
msgstr ""
"Quoi ! Je meurs ! Mais c'est impossible ! Le maître m'a toujours dit que je "
"serais l'un de ses généraux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:900
msgid ""
"You lived as a fool and shall die as one. Now let's see how much money your "
"master pays a fool."
msgstr ""
"Tu as vécu et tu es mort en idiot. Maintenant, voyons voir comment ton "
"maître récompense les imbéciles."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:905
msgid ""
"600 gold! Wow! The 'Master' must be an even greater fool then I thought!"
msgstr ""
"600 pièces d'or ! Ouaouh ! Le « Maître » doit être encore plus bête que ce "
"que je pensais !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:915
msgid ""
"You foolish humans! You shall all soon be meat for my wolves! REINFORCEMENTS!"
msgstr ""
"Humains stupides ! Vous serez bientôt de la viande pour mes loups ! "
"RENFORTS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06a_Old_Friend.cfg:974
msgid ""
"Come on, why are we just sitting here in these caves! Have you forgotten "
"already all these orcs have done to us! Let us muddy the ground with their "
"foul blood!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:4
msgid "Slave of the Undead"
msgstr "Esclave d'un mort-vivant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:8
msgid "Having completed his mission, Tallin reported back to his master."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir accompli sa mission, Tallin revint faire son rapport à son "
"maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:12
msgid ""
"Well done, my loyal slave. I see you have successfully completed your "
"mission."
msgstr ""
"Très bien, mon loyal esclave. Je vois que tu as parfaitement accompli ta "
"mission."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:17
msgid "Yes, master."
msgstr "Oui, maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:22
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Very well. Now, I have a new mission for you. Your old friends are becoming "
"a bit of an annoyance. Instead of just giving up as they should, they keep "
"foolishly attempting to attack me time and again. This time they have "
"attacked and seized one of the northern entrances. Although I can easily "
"defeat them as I have done several times when you were in training, this "
"time I want you to take care of them in a more...final way. Consider it a "
"test of your loyalty."
msgstr ""
"Très très bien. Maintenant, j'ai une autre mission pour toi. Tes vieux amis "
"commencent à m'ennuyer. Plutôt que de laisser tomber comme ils devraient le "
"faire, ils s'entêtent à m'attaquer régulièrement. Cette fois, ils ont pris "
"pour cible une des entrées au nord. Bien que je puisse facilement les "
"repousser, comme je l'ai déjà fait plusieurs fois durant ton entraînement, "
"cette fois je veux que tu t'en occupes d'une façon un peu plus ... "
"définitive. Considère cette mission comme un test de ta loyauté."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:27
msgid "...as you command ...Master."
msgstr "...vos désirs sont des ordres... Maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:32
msgid ""
"Good boy. Now, I am giving you the power to raise more powerful types of "
"undead. In addition, I will put under you command a few disembodied spirits "
"as well as some of my more promising adepts. Use them wisely. Now, go and "
"destroy those vermin!"
msgstr ""
"Brave garçon. Maintenant, je vais te donner le pouvoir de lever des morts-"
"vivants plus puissants. En plus je placerai sous ton commandement quelques "
"esprits désincarnés et mes adeptes les plus prometteurs. Utilise-les "
"sagement. Maintenant, va et détruis cette vermine !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:37
msgid ""
"Upon hearing the order of his master to kill his friends, something that had "
"been dormant inside Tallin these last few months revolted. But the magical "
"control that Malifor had over him was so great that he had no choice but to "
"obey his master. Thus, with his own will madly struggling to break free of "
"the lich, Talliln made his way to the northern entrance."
msgstr ""
"En entendant son maître lui ordonner de tuer ses anciens amis, quelque chose "
"d'endormi depuis des mois à l'intérieur de Tallin se révolta. Mais le "
"contrôle magique que Malifor avait sur lui était si fort qu'il n'avait pas "
"d'autre choix que d'obéir à son maître. C'est ainsi que Tallin se rendit à "
"l'entrée nord, contre sa volonté d'échapper au contrôle de la liche."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:54
msgid "Destroy the Invaders"
msgstr "Détruisez les intrus."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:262
msgid "James"
msgstr "James"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:271
msgid "Aledor"
msgstr "Aledor"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:279
msgid "My God! Tallin is that you?"
msgstr "Mon Dieu ! Tallin, c'est toi ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:285
msgid " $betrayed_friend.user_description, I..."
msgstr " $betrayed_friend.user_description, Je..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:290
msgid "Come on Tallin, talk to me!"
msgstr "Viens Tallin, parle-moi !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:296
msgid ".........."
msgstr "..........."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:301
msgid "Tallin, break free! Don't let that lich control you!"
msgstr "Tallin, échappe-toi ! Ne te laisse pas contrôler par cette liche !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:307
msgid "... KILL THE RABBLE!"
msgstr "... TUE CES IMBECILES !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:312
msgid "No, Tallin! Stop!"
msgstr "Tallin ! Non !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:317
msgid "Deaf to the calls of his friend, Tallin commenced the attack."
msgstr "Sourd aux appels de ses amis, Tallin lança l'attaque."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:344
msgid "What have I done..."
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que j'ai fais ... "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:370
msgid ""
"You fool! You have spared the humans and betrayed me! But I am not "
"concerned, I had already foreseen that possibility."
msgstr ""
"Imbécile ! Tu as épargné les humains et tu m'as trahi ! Mais ce n'est pas "
"grave, j'avais déjà prévu cette possibilité."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/06b_Slave_of_the_Undead.cfg:401
msgid "What the... everybody get out! The roof of the cave is collapsing!"
msgstr ""
"Qu'est-ce que... Tout le monde dehors ! Le plafond de la cave est en train "
"de s'effondrer !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:4
msgid "Settling Disputes"
msgstr "Règlement de comptes"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:9
msgid ""
"Tallin and his men made an orderly withdrawal into the caves, the orcs "
"pressing close behind them."
msgstr ""
"Tallin et ses hommes se retirèrent en bon ordre dans les cavernes. Les orcs "
"étaient sur leurs talons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:13
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dwarves were more then ready for them, however, and as soon as the "
"humans got through the defenses the well-prepared dwarves fell on the battle-"
"weary and bloodied orcs."
msgstr ""
"Les nains étaient cependant parfaitement organisés et prêts à les accueillir "
"et, dès que les humains eurent franchi les défenses, ils attaquèrent les "
"orcs déjà meurtris et ensanglantés."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Wave after wave of orcs crashed onto the dwarven defenses and shattered."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs s'écrasaient vague après vague sur les murailles naines et s'y "
"brisaient aussitôt."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:21
msgid "As the battle raged on, Tallin again made council with Hamel."
msgstr ""
"Tallin et Hamel tinrent une nouvelle fois conseil pendant que les combats "
"furieux se poursuivaient."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:25
msgid "How did ye fare?"
msgstr "Comment ça s'est passé ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:30
msgid ""
"It was fierce and bloody. We fought them for three days and nights with no "
"end in sight. Every time we killed an orc, it seemed that two more would "
"take his place. We most assuredly cannot win fighting like this."
msgstr ""
"Ce fut un combat acharné et sanglant. Nous les avons combattus quatre jours "
"et trois nuits, sans en voir la fin. Pour chaque orc abattu on aurait dit "
"que deux prenaient sa place. Une chose est certaine : nous ne gagnerons pas "
"de cette manière."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:35
msgid ""
"So you withdrew. Rightly done, me lad. Our prepared defenses will be able to "
"hold the orcs off far longer and with less loss then ye could ha' done in "
"the open field. I see that my training of you hasna' been for naught."
msgstr ""
"T'as bien fait de battre en retraite. Bonne décision, mon gars. Les défenses "
"que nous avons préparées s'ront capables de retenir les orcs bien plus "
"longtemps et avec moins de pertes que si vous étiez restés en terrain "
"découvert. Je vois qu'mon enseignement a servi à queq'chose."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:40
msgid ""
"And I am grateful - but what should we do from here? The number of humans "
"and dwarves is limited, unlike the orcs whose numbers seem unlimited."
msgstr ""
"Oui, et je t'en suis reconnaissant. Mais que devrions-nous faire à présent ? "
"Les humains et les nains sont en nombre limité, alors que les forces orcs "
"semblent inépuisables."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:45
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Aye. But we must utterly crush this orcish host if we are to ha' anything "
"other than a brief respite."
msgstr ""
"Ouaip. Mais nous d'vons écraser complètement cette armée orc pour pouvoir "
"espérer souffler plus de cinq minutes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:50
msgid ""
"Orcs are fickle; if we negotiated a treaty with them - assuming they would "
"accept - it would just be broken as soon as the next warlord arose among "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs sont versatiles ; si nous négocions un traité avec eux, en "
"supposant qu'ils l'acceptent, il sera rompu dès l'apparition d'un nouveau "
"chef de guerre orc."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:55
msgid ""
"Then what shall we do? Can we assassinate this Rakshas fellow and throw them "
"into disarray once more."
msgstr ""
"Que faire alors ? Ne pouvons-nous pas assassiner ce Rakshas d'une manière ou "
"d'une autre et les plonger à nouveau dans le chaos ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:60
msgid ""
"That will be very difficult. We did that last time and they will no doubt be "
"alert to that threat now. Anyway, it would be but temporary solution. Soon "
"another strong leader would emerge and we'd find oursel' back in the same "
"coil."
msgstr ""
"Ce sera très difficile. C'est ce qu'on a déjà fait et, cette fois, ils "
"feront certainement gaffe. De toute façon, ce n'est qu'une solution "
"temporaire. Un autre puissant chef ne tardera pas à surgir et tout "
"r'commencera."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:65
msgid "Well, back to the drawing board. What should we do?"
msgstr "Bon, retour à la case départ. Que faire ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:70
msgid ""
"I think we should try to gather more allies. That way we can engage them on "
"many fronts, or divide them into smaller groups, or cut them off from their "
"supplies. The possibilities are endless."
msgstr ""
"Je pense que nous devrions tenter de trouver de nouveaux alliés. Nous "
"pourrions ainsi lancer des assauts sur plusieurs fronts, essayer de les "
"diviser en petits groupes, ou encore leur couper leurs ravitaillements. Les "
"possibilités sont très nombreuses."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:75
msgid ""
"Wise words, but who is there in these wild Northlands that might aid us?"
msgstr ""
"Bien dit, mais qui pourrait nous aider dans les terres sauvages du Nord ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:80
msgid ""
"You can count the Elves out. They are a selfish lot, only interested in "
"themselves. They would only aid us if something drastic happened to them and "
"they needed our help. What about Wesnoth?"
msgstr ""
"On peut écarter les elfes. Ils sont très égoïstes et ne s'intéressent qu'à "
"eux. Ils ne nous aideraient que si quelque chose de terrible leur arrivait "
"et qu'ils avaient besoin de notre aide. Que penses-tu de Wesnoth ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:85
msgid ""
"Wesnoth is too far away, and we have no idea what political state they are "
"in."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth est trop éloigné et nous ignorons quel climat politique y règne."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:89
msgid ""
"The last news we heard of them was years ago when Prince Konrad passed "
"through here. At that time the evil queen Asheviere was ruling, and it was "
"said that she was in alliance with the orcs."
msgstr ""
"J'ai entendu parler d'eux pour la dernière fois il y a des années, quand le "
"Prince Konrad est passé par ici. À cette époque, la maléfique reine "
"Asheviere était au pouvoir et s'était apparemment alliée aux orcs."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:94
msgid ""
"And then that Princess Li'sar was in hot pursuit of Konrad as well. I wonder "
"what became of them."
msgstr ""
"Et la Princesse Li'sar était lancée dans une poursuite effrénée de Konrad. "
"Je me demande ce qu'il leur est arrivé."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:99
msgid ""
"The last time any dwarf set eyes on Konrad was when he set out to the "
"eastern tunnels in search of the Scepter of Fire, so he could claim his "
"place as ruler."
msgstr ""
"La dernière fois qu'un nain a vu Konrad, c'est quand il est parti pour les "
"tunnels de l'est à la recherche du Sceptre de Feu pour pouvoir prendre le "
"trône."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Geez, what a fool's quest. Everyone in these Northlands knows that the "
"Scepter is long gone."
msgstr ""
"Mazette, quelle quête insensée ! Tout le monde dans les Terres du Nord sait "
"bien que le Sceptre a disparu depuis longtemps."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:109
msgid ""
"But we're meandering. Where can we find allies in these wild Northlands?"
msgstr ""
"Mais ne nous égarons pas. Où pouvons-nous trouver des alliés dans les "
"sauvages Terres du Nord ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:114
msgid ""
"Tallin, before I was captured by Malifor, I used to be in contact with a "
"powerful magician called Ro'Arthian and his brother Ro'Sothian."
msgstr ""
"Tallin, avant d'être capturé par Malifor, j'étais en contact avec de "
"puissants magiciens nommés Ro'Arthian et Ro'Sothian, son frère."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:119
msgid "Ro'Arthian, pah! Don't utter that cursed name!"
msgstr "Ro'Arthian, peuh ! Ne prononcez pas ce nom maudit !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:124
msgid "Why not, Hamel, have you a grievance with him?"
msgstr "Pourquoi Hamel, quel est le problème ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:129
msgid ""
"I have heard all about him from my good friend Stalrag. He is - or was "
"anyway, haven't heard from him in years - the chief o' the villages that lay "
"along Highbrook Pass."
msgstr ""
"C'est mon vieil ami Stalrag qui m'a raconté tout ce que j'en sais. Il est, "
"ou plutôt était, car je n'ai pas eu de ses nouvelles depuis des années, chef "
"de plusieurs villages le long du Col du Haut-Rupt."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:134
msgid "Those foul mages have long terrorized Stalrag and his people."
msgstr "Ces sales mages terrorisent Stalrag et son peuple depuis longtemps."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:139
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Remember, Hamel, there are often two sides to a story like this. Perhaps the "
"mages see your dwarves as invaders. How would you feel if say... the elves "
"decided to come in and level Knalga so they can grow another big forest on "
"top?"
msgstr ""
"Souviens-toi Hamel, il y a toujours deux versions à chaque histoire. Peut-"
"être que les mages voient les nains comme des envahisseurs. Que dirais-tu si "
"par exemple... les elfes décidaient de venir ici pour aplanir Knalga et "
"planter une autre grande forêt dessus ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:144
msgid "Those filthy elves! I'll...."
msgstr "Ces elfes de m... ! Je vais leur..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:149
msgid "See!"
msgstr "Tu vois !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:154
msgid ""
"What were you doing keeping contact with mages such as those anyway? Trying "
"to save their souls?"
msgstr ""
"Pourquoi garder contact avec de tels mages, de toute façon ? Vous tentiez de "
"sauver leurs âmes ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:159
msgid " *giggle* Something like that."
msgstr "Eh eh, quelque chose comme ça."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/09a_Introductions.cfg:203
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:164
msgid " *rolls eyes*"
msgstr " *roule les yeux*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:169
msgid "Father Marcus, what are you trying to say?"
msgstr "Père Marcus, qu'essaies-tu de nous dire ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:174
msgid ""
"I propose that we go to Highbrook Pass and see how matters stand for "
"ourselves. If the wizards are still alive, we might be able to persuade them "
"to help us. What's more, if Stalrag is still around we could use his help "
"too."
msgstr ""
"Je propose de nous rendre au Col du Haut-Rupt et d'observer la situation. Si "
"les sorciers sont encore en vie, nous saurons peut-être les convaincre de "
"nous aider. Et si Stalrag est toujours dans le coin, son aide pourrait bien "
"nous être utile aussi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:179
msgid "I don't see how just two mages could help us very much, Father."
msgstr ""
"Je ne vois vraiment pas comment seulement deux mages pourraient nous aider, "
"mon Père."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:184
msgid ""
"They are not just any two mages. They have fine control over many creatures "
"of the wild such as ogres, gryphons, and sometimes even trolls! It would be "
"no bad thing to have those on your side for once."
msgstr ""
"Ce ne sont pas deux mages insignifiants. Ils exercent également un grand "
"contrôle sur les créatures sauvages comme les ogres, les griffons ou même "
"les trolls ! Pour une fois, ce serait plutôt bien de les avoir de notre côté."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:189
msgid "That sounds really good. What do you think, Hamel?"
msgstr "C'est tentant. Qu'en penses-tu Hamel ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Hrmph. These are desperate times. If those lunatics of mages will agree to "
"help, I guess we'll nae have any other choice but to accept."
msgstr ""
"Humpf. On est dans le pétrin jusqu'au cou. La fin justifie les moyens, si "
"ces fous de mage acceptent de nous aider, j'crois qu'on peut qu'accepter."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:199
msgid ""
"Hey, we have had experiences with crazy mages ourselves. Believe me, they "
"are dangerous! You will feel a lot better with some of them on your side."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons vu à l'œuvre des magiciens fous. Eh bien crois-moi, ils sont "
"dangereux ! Mieux vaut en avoir quelques-uns dans ton camp."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:204
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ye'll need to travel light to reach Highbrook Pass before the orcs mount "
"another assault in force. I think ye should just take as much gold as you "
"think ye'll need and leave the rest here. We'll store it in the tunnels "
"furthest away from the attacking orcs in case they manage to break thorugh."
msgstr ""
"Tu vas d'voir voyager léger pour atteindre le Col du Haut-Rupt avant que les "
"orcs ne lancent un autre assaut. J'crois que tu d'vrais prendre tout l'or "
"qui risque de te servir, et laisser le reste ici. Nous l'entreposerons dans "
"les galeries hors de portée des orcs, juste au cas où ils arriveraient à "
"traverser nos défenses."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:209
msgid "So it shall be. Now how exactly do we get to this mountain pass?"
msgstr "Bonne idée. Alors, comment se aller à ce col ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:214
msgid "And so Tallin and his party set out to secure the help of the mages."
msgstr ""
"C'est ainsi que Tallin et sa bande partirent chercher l'aide des mages."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:267
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:250
msgid "Stalrag"
msgstr "Stalrag"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:307
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:281
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:271
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:170
msgid "Ro'Arthian"
msgstr "Ro'Arthian."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:294
msgid "Save Stalrag from Ro'Sothian."
msgstr "Protéger Stalrag de Ro'Sothian."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:298
msgid "Death of Tallin or Stalrag."
msgstr "Mort de Tallin ou de Stalrag."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:353
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:294
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:363
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:861
msgid "Ro'Sothian"
msgstr "Ro'Sothian"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:466
msgid ""
"Upon arriving at the mountain pass it appeared to Tallin and his men that "
"they were just a bit too late."
msgstr ""
"Arrivés au col, Tallin et ses hommes virent qu'ils arrivaient un petit peu "
"trop tard."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:472
msgid "HAH! I finally have you, you wretched dwarf!"
msgstr "Aha ! Je te tiens enfin, misérable nain !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:477
msgid ""
"Argh! You blasted mages! How many times do I have to kill you two before you "
"will leave us in peace!"
msgstr ""
"Argh ! Maudits mages ! Combien de fois devrai-je vous tuer tous les deux "
"avant que vous ne nous laissiez en paix !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Leave YOU in peace! It is your kind that won't leave US in peace. Ever since "
"you blasted dwarves built that damn road you have harassed us unceasingly! "
"Now, it ends here! After I kill you I will split your carcass and hang it at "
"the mouth of this pass as a warning for any other fools like you! And unlike "
"us you WON'T come back."
msgstr ""
"VOUS laisser en paix ! C'est votre espèce qui ne NOUS laisse pas en paix. "
"Depuis que votre engeance damnée a construit cette maudite route, vous "
"n'avez eu de cesse de nous harceler ! Mais cela va prendre fin ici et "
"maintenant ! Une fois que je t'aurai tué, j'ouvrirai ta carcasse et "
"l'exposerai à l'entrée de ce col pour avertir les imbéciles de ton genre ! "
"Et contrairement à nous, tu ne reviendras PAS."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:487
msgid ""
"You cursed mage! I now go to join all of my men you have killed. But know "
"this, the Shinsplitters will NEVER submit! We will defy you to our last "
"breath!"
msgstr ""
"Très bien, maudit mage ! Je m'en vais maintenant rejoindre tous ceux que "
"vous avez tués. Mais sache que les Brisetibias n'abandonneront JAMAIS ! Nous "
"vous défierons jusqu'à notre dernier souffle !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:492
msgid "Hold it! What's going on here!"
msgstr "Attendez ! Que se passe-t-il ici !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:497
msgid "Ro'Sothian, is that you?"
msgstr "Ro'Sothian, c'est toi ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:502
msgid "Not now, Father. I'm a little busy at the moment."
msgstr "Pas maintenant, mon Père. Je suis un peu occupé pour l'instant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:526
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:632
msgid "Hang on a sec, Ro'Sothian, you don't want to kill him."
msgstr "Attends un peu Ro'Sothian, tu ne vas quand même pas le tuer ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:531
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:637
msgid "Huh!? He killed me!"
msgstr "Hein ? Il m'a bien tué, lui !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:536
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh.... I see. Ro'Sothian, we come on more pressing business. We are in "
"desperate need of your help. Here is Tallin, from the community of Dwarven "
"Doors. As you know, the people of Dwarven Doors were enslaved by the orcs "
"for many years. They have broken their chains, and together with Lord Hamel "
"from Knalga, they are beginning to reclaim Knalga from the night of chaos."
msgstr ""
"Ah... je vois. Quoi qu'il en soit Ro'Sothian, nous avons terriblement besoin "
"de ton aide. Voici Tallin de la communauté des Portes des Nains. Comme tu le "
"sais, les gens des Portes des Nains étaient asservis par les orcs depuis de "
"nombreuses années. Ils ont réussi à se libérer et, avec le Seigneur Hamel de "
"Knalga, ils commencent à sortir Knalga du chaos dans lequel la nation était "
"plongée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:541
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:647
msgid ""
"So? What does this have to do with me? And hurry up, my staff is buzzing to "
"blast this little vermin once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Et alors ? Qu'est-ce que ça peut me faire ? Et dépêchez-vous, mon bâton "
"vrombit à l'idée de réduire à néant cette petite vermine, une bonne fois "
"pour toutes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:546
msgid ""
"Don't! Please, my friend, listen. The orcs are on the rise again and they "
"are threatening to complete their conquest of Knalga and convert it into an "
"orcish stronghold. We can't let that happen! That's why we have come here, "
"to seek yours and your brother's help in defeating the orcs."
msgstr ""
"Non ! Écoute mon ami, s'il te plaît. Les orcs se sont de nouveau sur le pied "
"de guerre et risquent de conquérir Knalga pour la convertir en forteresse "
"orc. Nous ne pouvons pas laisser cela se produire ! Nous sommes venus ici "
"pour te demander ton aide et celle de ton frère, pour vaincre les orcs."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:551
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Take your begging and shove it, Father! We don't help no-one. Not even you "
"and ESPECIALLY not any dwarf!"
msgstr ""
"Mon Père, vous pouvez vous asseoir sur vos doléances ! Nous n'aidons "
"personne. Pas même vous et SURTOUT pas les nains !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:556
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I tire of this. Prepare to die, dwarf! And the rest of you, get lost and "
"don't come back, unless you're anxious to meet your makers!"
msgstr ""
"Et puis cette conversation me fatigue ; prépare-toi à mourir, nain ! Et vous "
"autres, allez voir ailleurs si j'y suis et ne revenez pas, sauf si vous êtes "
"pressés de rencontrer vos créateurs !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:561
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:677
msgid "Uh oh, he is gathering energy for a cold blast."
msgstr "Oh oh, il rassemble de l'énergie pour lancer une onde glaciale."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:566
msgid "Quick, Theta, we've got to stop him. Let's go!"
msgstr "Vite Theta, nous devons l'arrêter. Allons-y !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:607
msgid ""
"Ro'Sothian! How are you doing, my old friend! Boy, you sure look... erm.... "
"different!"
msgstr ""
"Ro'Sothian ! Comment vas-tu, mon vieil ami ! Oh mon Dieu, tu parais "
"vraiment... hem... différent !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:612
msgid ""
"Camerin! Great Lords of Darkness, I haven't seen you in ages! Here, let me "
"just finish off this little vermin and I'll be right over."
msgstr ""
"Camerin ! Par tous les puissants seigneurs des ténèbres, je ne t'avais pas "
"vu depuis des lustres ! Allez, laisse-moi juste me débarrasser de cette "
"vermine et je suis à toi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:617
msgid " *aside* Camerin, you know him?"
msgstr " *à part* Camerin, tu le connais ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:622
msgid " *aside* Duh! His brother Ro'Arthian is the one who taught me magic!"
msgstr " *à part* Bah ! C'est son frère Ro'Arthian qui m'a enseigné la magie !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:627
msgid " *aside* Oh....!"
msgstr " *à part* Oh... !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:642
msgid ""
"Oh.... I see. But we come on more pressing business. We are in desperate "
"need of your help. Here is Tallin from the community of Dwarven Doors. As "
"you know, the people of Dwarven Doors were enslaved by the orcs for many "
"years. They have broken their chains and together with Lord Hamel from "
"Knalga, they are beginning to reclaim Knalga from the chaos that it was in."
msgstr ""
"Ah... je vois. Quoi qu'il en soit Ro'Sothian, nous avons terriblement besoin "
"de ton aide. Voici Tallin de la communauté des Portes des Nains. Comme tu le "
"sais, les gens des Portes des Nains étaient asservis par les orcs depuis de "
"nombreuses années. Ils ont réussi à se libérer et, avec le Seigneur Hamel de "
"Knalga, ils commencent à sortir Knalga du chaos dans lequel la nation était "
"plongée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:652
msgid ""
"Don't! Please, my friend, listen. The orcs are on the rise again and they "
"are threatening to complete their conquest of Knalga and convert it into an "
"orcish stronghold. We can't let that happen! That's why we have come here, "
"to seek yours and your brothers help in defeating the orcs."
msgstr ""
"Non ! Écoute mon ami, s'il te plaît. Les orcs se relèvent et risquent "
"d'achever leur conquête de Knalga et de la transformer en une de leur "
"forteresse. Nous ne pouvons pas laisser cela se produire ! Nous sommes donc "
"venus ici pour te demander ton aide et celle de ton frère pour vaincre les "
"orcs."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:662
msgid ""
"Hold a mement, my friend. You won't believe what a blast it is fighting with "
"these guys. You get to fry skeletons, orcs, trolls, and wolves by the "
"thousands! Come on old pal, be a sport."
msgstr ""
"Attends une seconde, mon ami. Tu n'imagines pas comme on s'éclate en "
"combattant avec ces gars-là. Tu dois faire frire des squelettes, des orcs, "
"des trolls et des loups par milliers ! Allez mon pote, sois sympa !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Camerin, you were always a little crazy. Now I see you have gone stark "
"raving mad! Do you really think we would help anyone? ESPECIALLY a bunch of "
"dwarves!"
msgstr ""
"Camerin, tu as toujours été un peu fou. Mais je vois que maintenant tu es "
"devenu complètement cinglé ! Pense-tu vraiment que nous allons aider "
"quelqu'un ? Et SURTOUT des nains !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:672
msgid ""
"I tire of this; prepare to die, wretched dwarf! And the rest of you, get "
"lost and don't come back, unless you're tired of life!"
msgstr ""
"De toute manière, je suis fatigué de cette conversation ; prépare-toi à "
"mourir, nain ! Quant à vous autres, allez vous faire voir et ne revenez pas, "
"à moins d'être fatigués de la vie !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:682
msgid "Quick, honey, we've got to stop him. Let's go!"
msgstr "Vite ma tendre, nous devons l'arrêter. Allons-y !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:687
msgid "Hey, are you two going to hog all the fun for yourselves?"
msgstr "Hé ! Vous ne pensez quand même pas être les seuls à vous amuser ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:692
msgid "Alright, alright, hang on!"
msgstr "Ok, c'est bon, tiens bon !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:750
msgid "BROTHER! HELP ME!"
msgstr "FRÈRE ! À L'AIDE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:755
msgid ""
" *booming voice coming from all directions* SO YOU MAGES HAVE THE AUDACITY "
"TO ATTACK MY BROTHER! YOU SHALL DIE FOR YOUR FOLLY!"
msgstr ""
" *voix tonnante semblant provenir de toutes parts* MAGES, VOUS AVEZ L'AUDACE "
"D'ATTAQUER MON FRÈRE ! VOUS ALLEZ PAYER POUR CETTE FOLIE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:760
msgid ""
"Ro'Arthian, listen to me. We don't want to fight with you, we have come here "
"to seek your assistance."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Arthian, écoute-moi. Nous ne sommes pas venus nous battre contre vous, au "
"contraire nous venons vous prier de nous aider."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:765
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:776
msgid "No answer"
msgstr "Pas de réponse"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:771
msgid ""
"I know you can hear me, Ro'Arthian. Please, the fate of every creature in "
"the north depends on your help."
msgstr ""
"Je sais que tu peux m'entendre, Ro'Arthian. S'il vous plaît, le sort de "
"toutes les créatures du Nord dépend de toi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Give it up, father, he isn't answering. I am afraid we may have to use um... "
"more forceful means to convince him."
msgstr ""
"Laissez tomber, mon Père, il ne répond pas. J'ai bien peur que nous devions "
"utiliser hum... des moyens plus énergiques pour le convaincre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:787
msgid " *sigh* Yes, you are right."
msgstr " *soupir* Tu as sûrement raison."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:792
msgid "Put Ro'Sothian into that jail over there until we capture his brother."
msgstr ""
"Enfermez Ro'Sothian dans cette cellule jusqu'à ce que nous ayons capturé son "
"frère."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:805
msgid "And someone keep an eye on him. We don't want him to get away."
msgstr ""
"Et que quelqu'un garde un œil sur lui. Il ne doit surtout pas s'échapper."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:817
msgid "Capture Ro'Arthian."
msgstr "Capturer Ro'Arthian."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:825
msgid "Death of Stalrag."
msgstr "Mort de Stalrag."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:869
msgid "Ha! I am free! Now you foul traitors will pay!"
msgstr "Ha ! Je suis libre ! Très bien, vous allez payer, sales traîtres !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:874
msgid "Oh no, he got away! Quick, men, we must capture him again!"
msgstr ""
"Oh non, il s'est enfui ! Vite soldats, nous devons le capturer derechef !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:891
msgid "Ahhhh! Not again!"
msgstr "Ah non, pas encore !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:896
msgid ""
"Come on, Ro'Sothian, we really don't have to be doing this. Come, join us!"
msgstr ""
"Allez Ro'Sothian, on n'est vraiment pas obligé de faire ça. Viens, rejoins-"
"nous !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:901
msgid "Never!"
msgstr "Jamais !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:906
msgid "Sigh, we'll talk later."
msgstr "Pfff, on en reparlera plus tard."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:911
msgid "Back to jail, my friend."
msgstr "Retour en prison, l'ami."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:936
msgid "Ro'Arthian, are you ready to talk yet?"
msgstr "Ro'Arthian, êtes-vous prêt à discuter à présent ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:941
msgid "Fine, you trespassers. What do you want?"
msgstr "Très bien, intrus. Que voulez-vous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:946
msgid "Well... first why don't you tell us what you want?"
msgstr "Eh bien... si vous nous disiez d'abord ce que, vous, vous voulez ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:951
msgid ""
"What do I want? I'll tell you what I want! I want the stinking carcasses of "
"you, all your henchmen and those dwarvish vermin off of my land! And STAY "
"off!"
msgstr ""
"Ce que je veux ? Je vais te dire ce que je veux ! Je veux voir ta carcasse "
"puante, celles de tes sbires et celles de ces vermines naines dégager hors "
"de ma propriété ! ET N'Y REVENEZ PAS !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:956
msgid "So basically, you want to be left alone in peace. Right?"
msgstr ""
"Donc en gros, vous voulez qu'on vous laisse tranquille. C'est bien ça ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:961
#, fuzzy
msgid "Wow! Someone FINALLY figured it out!"
msgstr " *mots dégoulinant de sarcasme* Waouh ! Quelqu'un a ENFIN compris !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:966
msgid ""
"Alright! Listen then. Right now we have very little power to grant your "
"request. We are simply a band of peasants fighting for the freedom of our "
"homeland."
msgstr ""
"Très bien ! Écoutez alors. Là, on n'a pas franchement les moyens de vous "
"accorder cette requête. Nous ne sommes qu'une bande de paysans qui essaient "
"de se battre pour délivrer leurs terres."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:971
msgid ""
"But when we defeat the orcish host, re-establish Knalga, and bring law and "
"order into these Northlands, we will have gained some authority by right of "
"conquest."
msgstr ""
"Mais quand on aura réussi à vaincre les hordes orcs, à restaurer Knalga et à "
"ramener la sécurité dans les Terres du Nord, je suis sûr qu'alors nous "
"aurons un minimum d'autorité."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:976
msgid ""
"When that time comes, I hereby make a solemn oath: no man or dwarf shall "
"ever set foot on your land without your leave. If any of my men violates "
"this law they shall be punished with death, and I believe I may speak for "
"Hamel in this as well."
msgstr ""
"Quand ce temps sera venu, j'en fais dès à présent le serment solennel : "
"aucun homme ni aucun nain ne devra jamais mettre le pied sur vos terres sans "
"votre accord. Si un de mes hommes viole cette loi, il sera châtié par la "
"mort, et je suis sûr que Hamel en fera autant."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:981
msgid ""
"In order for that to come about, we must crush the orcish host. But we can't "
"do that without your help. Will you join us?"
msgstr ""
"Néanmoins, Ro'Arthian, pour que cela se déroule ainsi, nous devons anéantir "
"les cohortes orcs. Mais nous n'y arriverons pas sans votre aide. Vous "
"joindrez-vous à nous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:986
msgid ""
"Think of it, Ro'Arthian, it is a fair bargain. If you don't agree to "
"Tallin's proposal, the endless war you two wage with the dwarves will never "
"be resolved. You have been haunting these mountains for far too long. It is "
"high time for you and your brother to rest in peace."
msgstr ""
"Réfléchissez Ro'Arthian, c'est un marché honnête. Si vous refusez la "
"proposition de Tallin, alors la guerre entre les nains et vous ne s'achèvera "
"jamais. Vous avez hanté ces montagnes pendant beaucoup trop longtemps. Il "
"est grand temps que vous et votre frère reposiez en paix."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:991
msgid "Hrmph. What do you think, brother?"
msgstr "Humpf. Qu'en dis-tu, frère ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1009
msgid " *shrugs* I don't think we have any other choice left."
msgstr ""
" *haussement d'épaules* Je ne pense pas que nous ayons vraiment le choix."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1014
msgid ""
"Come on, guys, it will be great! Those orcs will never know what hit them! "
"Together we'll rip them to shreds! If you are planning to retire after this, "
"this is the perfect chance for you guys to go out with a bang! You guys will "
"become legends! 'The two terrible mages, risen from the dead to devastate "
"the orcish hordes!'"
msgstr ""
"Allez les gars, ça va être super ! Les orcs ne vont pas comprendre ce qui "
"leur tombe dessus ! Ensemble, nous les mettrons en lambeaux ! Si vous "
"prévoyez de vous retirer du monde après cela, c'est l'occasion idéale pour "
"prendre le large avec panache ! Vous allez devenir des légendes, les gars ! "
"« Les deux mages terribles, revenus du monde des morts pour dévaster les "
"hordes d'orcs ! »"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1019
msgid ""
"Very well, Tallin. We accept under the terms that your people will forever "
"leave us in peace after this."
msgstr ""
"Très bien Tallin. Nous acceptons, à condition que votre peuple nous laisse "
"en paix pour toujours après ceci."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1024
msgid ""
"Ro'Arthian, I am not of royal blood, but I am a man of my word. I will "
"uphold the oath I have given even at the cost of my life."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Arthian, je ne suis pas de sang royal mais je suis un homme de parole. Je "
"ne briserai pas mon serment même si cela doit me coûter la vie."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1029
msgid "Very well. The orcish hosts shall feel our wrath!"
msgstr "Très bien. Les armées orcs sentiront notre colère !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1034
msgid ""
"Wait a second, Tallin. Are you saying that we should abandon our homeland to "
"these wretched mages!?"
msgstr ""
"Attends une minute, Tallin. Es-tu en train de dire que nous devrions "
"abandonner nos terres à ces mages infâmes !?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:580
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1082
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:794
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1039
msgid " *snicker*"
msgstr " *ricanements*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1044
msgid ""
"Chief Stalrag, it is said that to save a family, we should be willing to "
"sacrifice one person; to save a town we should be willing to sacrifice a "
"family; and to save a nation we should be willing to sacrifice a town."
msgstr ""
"Écoute Stalrag. On dit que pour sauver une famille, nous devrions consentir "
"à sacrifier une personne ; que pour sauver une ville, nous devrions "
"consentir à sacrifier une famille ; et que pour sauver une nation, nous "
"devrions consentir à sacrifier une ville."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1049
msgid "Now, Stalrag, it is up to you. Do you want to save Knalga or not?"
msgstr "Stalrag, c'est donc à toi de voir. Veux-tu sauver Knalga ou non ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1054
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well Tallin, if you put it that way... We don't like it, but if that's what "
"is needed to save Knalga, we shall do it."
msgstr ""
" *regard furieux vers Ro'Arthian* Très bien, Tallin. Nous n'aimons pas ça, "
"mais si c'est ce qu'il faut pour sauver Knalga, nous le ferons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1059
msgid ""
"Thank you, Stalrag. I am sure that the sacrifice of you and your people will "
"always be remembered."
msgstr "Merci Stalrag. Je suis sûr que votre sacrifice ne sera jamais oublié."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1064
#, fuzzy
msgid " *mumbles* Yeah, great compensation..."
msgstr " *en marmonnant* Ce n'est pas une grande consolation !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1069
msgid ""
"I have the power to control many creatures, such as Gryphons, Trolls and "
"Ogres. So while I am with you you they shall be at your command."
msgstr ""
"Quoi qu'il en soit Tallin, j'ai pensé que vous devriez savoir que j'ai le "
"pouvoir de contrôler de nombreuses créatures, comme les griffons, les trolls "
"et les ogres. Aussi, tant que je suis avec vous vous pouvez les recruter. "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1074
msgid "The Shinsplitters will be at your service, Tallin."
msgstr "Les Brisetibias seront aussi à votre service, Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1079
msgid ""
"My thanks, Stalrag and Ro'Arthian. However, I have sufficient forces under "
"my control presently and I think that merging our forces will just create "
"confusion. Your gryphons will be of use, but I think you should retain "
"command of your trolls and ogres, until they are needed."
msgstr ""
"Merci, Stalrag et Ro'Arthian. Quoiqu'il en soit, j'ai suffisamment de forces "
"sous contrôle à présent, et je pense que rassembler nos force ne pourra que "
"créer la confusion. Vos griffons seront utiles, mais je pense que vous "
"devriez garder le commandement de vos trolls et de vos ogres, jusqu'à ce "
"qu'on en ait besoin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1089
msgid ""
"Great. Now let's get back to the caves and start planning the best way teach "
"those orcs a lesson they will never forget!"
msgstr ""
"Génial ! Maintenant retournons aux cavernes et commençons à réfléchir à la "
"meilleure manière de donner à ces orcs une leçon qu'ils n'oublieront pas de "
"sitôt !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1109
msgid "Farewell, my friends. I now go to join my fallen brethren."
msgstr ""
"Adieu, mes amis. Je rejoins à présent mes frères tombés au champ d'honneur."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07a_Settling_Disputes.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"No! If Stalrag dies now none of his men will follow us. We are finished."
msgstr ""
"Non ! Si Stalrag meurt maintenant, aucun des siens ne voudra nous suivre. "
"Nous sommes foutus."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:4
msgid "Protecting the Master"
msgstr "Protéger le maître"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:17
msgid ""
"As Tallin sat staring blankly at the body of his former friend - loathing "
"and hating what he had become - he received an urgent summons from his "
"Master."
msgstr ""
"Tallin s'était assis, scrutant le corps de son ancien ami d'un regard "
"absent. Il se répugnait, il détestait ce qu'il était devenu. Il reçu alors "
"un rappel urgent de son maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The attack Tallin had been sent to thwart had been a decoy. While Tallin was "
"away, Tallin's former friends had attacked Malifor's study with overwhelming "
"force."
msgstr ""
"L'attaque que Tallin devait contrecarrer s'était avéré être une diversion. "
"Profitant de son éloignement, ses anciens amis avaient attaqué massivement "
"l'étude de Malifor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:25
msgid ""
"Although Tallin was glad in his heart to see Malifor in such distress, the "
"sorcerous geas on his mind compelled him to go to his Master's aid. When he "
"got there, he found that all the outer defenses had been smashed and Malifor "
"had bolted himself up in his study. Bound by the will of their Master, "
"Tallin and his minions took up positions outside Malifor's study door."
msgstr ""
"Tallin était secrètement heureux de voir Malifor en si grande détresse, mais "
"la compulsion magique qui était en lui l'obligeait à voler au secours de son "
"maître. Quand il arriva, il vit que toutes les défenses extérieures avaient "
"été abattues et que Malifor s'était enfermé dans son étude. Obéissant à la "
"volonté de son maître, Tallin et ses subalternes prirent position pour "
"protéger la porte du repaire de Malifor."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:37
msgid "Resist Till the End of Turns"
msgstr "Résister jusqu'à la fin des tours."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:341
msgid "Look, the traitor Tallin has come to protect his master."
msgstr "Regardez, Tallin le traître est venu protéger son maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:347
msgid " Camerin! Please get out of here. Don't make me kill you too."
msgstr ""
"Camerin ! S'il te plaît, ne reste pas là. Ne m'oblige pas à te tuer aussi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:352
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fat chance, buddy. I can handle the likes of you in my sleep. Fall on them, "
"boys!"
msgstr ""
"Pas de chance, mon pote. Je ne peux pas blairer des types comme vous. Sus à "
"l'ennemi, les gars !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08b_Ray_of_Hope.cfg:512
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:365
msgid "At last, I am free..."
msgstr "Au moins, je suis libre..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:378
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:585
msgid " *BOOM!*"
msgstr " *BOUM !*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:424
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:633
msgid "What the.... NO!!!"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que... NON !!! "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:429
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:638
msgid "HEEEEE-YAAAAA!!!"
msgstr "HEEEEE-YAAAAA!!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:454
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:663
msgid ""
"CURSES ON YOU YOU BLASTED MAGES, CURSES ON YOU YOU BLASTED HUMANS, CURSES ON "
"YOU YOU BLASTED DWARVES! MAY YOUR MISERABLE LIVES BE FULL OF TORTURE! MAY "
"YOUR PEOPLE NEVER BE FREE! MAY ALL YOUR NEAR AND DEAR DESERT YOU! MAY A "
"THUNDERBOLT HIT YOUR HEAD! MAY..."
msgstr ""
"SOYEZ MAUDITS, SALES MAGES ! SOYEZ MAUDITS, SALES HUMAINS, SOYEZ MAUDITS, "
"SALES NAINS ! QUE VOS MISÉRABLES VIES NE SOIENT PLUS QU'UNE LONGUE SUITE DE "
"TORTURES ! QUE VOS GENS NE SOIENT JAMAIS LIBRES ! QUE CEUX QUI VOUS SONT "
"PROCHES ET CHERS VOUS ABANDONNENT ! QUE LA FOUDRE FRAPPE VOS TÊTES ! QUE..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:480
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:694
msgid ""
"Malifor is dead... what have I done? What am I going to do? I must flee this "
"place!"
msgstr ""
"Malifor est mort... qu'est-ce que j'ai fait ? Que vais-je devenir ? Je dois "
"quitter cet endroit !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:485
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:699
msgid "Hey, there goes the traitor Tallin!"
msgstr "Hé, Tallin le traître s'enfuit par là !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:490
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:704
msgid ""
"Let him go. He was not acting under his free will and thus there is no blame "
"attached to him. I have known of many such poor souls. If he does trouble us "
"in the future, however, we should not spare him."
msgstr ""
"Laissez-le partir. Il n'agissait pas selon son libre arbitre et nous ne "
"pouvons blâmer ses actes. J'ai connu beaucoup de ces pauvres âmes. Mais nous "
"ne devrons pas l'épargner s'il nous cause d'autres problèmes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Besides, he will probably just go and drown himself in the nearest river "
"anyway, so why bother killing him?"
msgstr ""
"De toute façon, il va sûrement se jeter dans la rivière la plus proche, ça "
"ne vaut pas la peine de le tuer nous-même !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:511
msgid "Ahhh! Master, help me!"
msgstr "Ahhh ! Maître, aidez-moi !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:516
#, fuzzy
msgid "Serves you right, you useless excuse for a slave."
msgstr "Débrouille-toi, espèce de vieux débris inutile."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:530
msgid "Master! Tallin is taking my villages!"
msgstr "Maître ! Tallin s'empare de mes villages !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:536
msgid "Shut up, you idiot. I know what I am doing."
msgstr "Tais-toi, idiot. Je sais ce que je fais."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:541
msgid ""
"Agreed. And if you don't keep your mouth shut, I will personally shut it for "
"you!"
msgstr ""
"D'accord. Et si tu ne la fermes pas, je m'occuperai de toi personnellement !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:546
msgid " *Gulp*"
msgstr " *Gloups*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:561
msgid ""
"Hmmm, you aren't as bad as I thought, Tallin. Unfortunately for you, we "
"aren't ready to give up just yet."
msgstr ""
"Hmmm, tu n'es pas si mauvais que je ne le pensais, Tallin. Malheureusement "
"pour toi, nous ne sommes pas encore prêts à abandonner."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:688
msgid "Pew! Nick of time too - I almost bought it there!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/07b_Protecting_the_Master.cfg:709
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Besides, he will probably just go and drown himself in the nearest river "
"anyway, so why bother?"
msgstr ""
"De toute façon, il va sûrement se jeter dans la rivière la plus proche, ça "
"ne vaut pas la peine de le tuer nous-même !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:4
msgid "Elvish Princess"
msgstr "Princesse elfe"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:9
msgid ""
"After securing the help of the two lich-mages, the party returned to Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir obtenu l'aide des mages (ou plutôt des liches), la bande "
"retourna à Knalga."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Och, that was a piece o' good work, lad, getting both the lich-mages and "
"Stalrag on our side. Now let's plan our way to bringing Rakshas down..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, ça mon ami, bien joué pour nous avoir rallié deux mages-liches et "
"Stalrag. Maintenant, préparons nos plans pour renverser Rakshas."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The lich-mages sent forth gryphons to scout out the number, formation and "
"deployment of the orcish forces, and to seek allies as well."
msgstr ""
"Les liches envoyèrent immédiatement des griffons pour épier le nombre, la "
"formation et l'organisation des forces orcs, et pour essayer de dénicher un "
"allié potentiel."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:22
msgid ""
"One day a gryphon came screeching into the caves with the news that a large "
"elvish force approached from the east. Messages were quickly dispatched to "
"the elves asking their purpose. The haughty reply was that their purpose was "
"none of any dwarf's or human's business, and that all would be well-advised "
"to stay in their holes when the elves passed near."
msgstr ""
"Un jour, un griffon arriva en criaillant dans les cavernes pour signaler une "
"importante force elfe qui venait de l'est dans leur direction. Des missives "
"furent rapidement envoyées pour savoir leurs intentions. La réponse hautaine "
"qui leur parvint fut que cela ne concernait aucun nain ou humain et qu'ils "
"feraient mieux de rester dans leurs trous quand les elfes passeraient dans "
"les parages."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Before the humans and dwarves could respond to this message, another gryphon "
"arrived with the news that the orcs were holding an elvish sorceress "
"prisoner in the castle of Bitterhold, less than a day's march distant to the "
"northwest. The castle had attracted notice because it had been recently "
"rebuilt and manned by a unit known to include some of the hardiest and "
"toughest of veteran orcs."
msgstr ""
"Avant même que les humains et les nains puissent répondre, un autre griffon "
"rapporta la nouvelle que les orcs tenaient prisonnière une sorcière elfe au "
"château de Castel Amer, à moins d'un jour de marche au nord-ouest. Le "
"château avait attiré l'attention car il avait été récemment rénové et était "
"occupé par une troupe connue pour inclure quelques-uns vétérans orcs les "
"plus féroces et les plus endurcis ."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:30
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gryphons and a picked force of human woodsmen were sent out that very night, "
"and less than two days later managed to ambush an orcish messenger on the "
"road out of Bitterhold. The messenger was carrying a ransom demand to the "
"elves - for the sorceress was, in fact, a princess of the highest rank."
msgstr ""
"Des griffons et une des hommes des bois bien sélectionnés furent envoyés "
"cette nuit là, et réussirent, moins de deux jours plus tard, à tendre une "
"embuscade à un messager orc sur la route de Castel Amer. Il portait une "
"demande de rançon à destination des elfes - car la sorcière était, en "
"réalité, une princesse du plus haut rang."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:34
msgid "The leaders met in council, considering what to do..."
msgstr "Les chefs tinrent conseil pour décider quoi faire..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:38
msgid ""
"This kidnapped princess explains a great deal. It is not easy to draw the "
"elves out of their forests."
msgstr ""
"Une princesse kidnappée veut dire une grosse négociation. Il n'est pas "
"facile de faire sortir les elfes de leurs forêts."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:43
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Aye, lad. Her kin will have come either to do battle or pay ransom. By the "
"looks of things, they've busked themselves for either."
msgstr ""
"Ouais, mon ami. Sa race viendra. Pour se battre ou pour payer la rançon. "
"D'après ce qu'on sait, ils se sont préparés aux deux alternatives."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:48
msgid ""
"Pahhh, who cares. Let the elves and orcs chop each other into mincemeat. It "
"will just make things easier for us."
msgstr ""
"Bahh, peu importe. Laissons les elfes et les orcs se tailler en pièces, ça "
"nous facilitera le travail."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:53
msgid ""
"Hah! I ken yer brain has rotted awa' entire. Think on it, skull-head, what "
"would happen if the elves dinna fight and pay the ransom instead?"
msgstr ""
"Ha ! Je vois que ta cervelle a fini de se décomposer. Réfléchis un peu, "
"crâne vide, qu'est-ce qui se passerait si les elfes payaient la rançon au "
"lieu de se battre ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:58
msgid "Do you want to die, dwarf?"
msgstr "Tu veux mourir, nain ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:63
msgid ""
"Peace, peace! If you two want to kill something, there are plenty of orcs "
"outside."
msgstr ""
"S'il vous plaît, du calme ! Si vous avez envie de tuer quelqu'un, il y a des "
"tas d'orcs à l'extérieur."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:68
msgid ""
"But you do have a point, Stalrag, That ransom will buy more troops and "
"weapons for the orcs, worse news for us."
msgstr ""
"Mais tu as raison sur un point, Stalrag, cette rançon procurera encore plus "
"de troupes et d'armes aux orcs, ce qui est une mauvaise nouvelle pour nous."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:73
msgid "I think we have a chance to make new some allies here..."
msgstr "Je pense que nous avons une chance de nous faire de nouveaux alliés..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:78
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Allies? I take it we're to go to them and ask them to join us in return for "
"our help in rescuing their Princess? You heard their message - those elves "
"have got their noses so high in the air they canna see over them. They "
"wouldna ally themsel' with the likes o' us."
msgstr ""
"Des alliés ? Je nous vois bien aller les voir et leur demander de nous "
"rallier en remerciement de notre aide pour avoir sauvé leur princesse ? Tu "
"as compris leur message ; ces elfes ont une si haute opinion d'eux-mêmes "
"qu'ils daignent à peine poser un regard sur nous... Ils ne voudront pas "
"s'allier avec des gens comme *nous*."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:83
msgid ""
"Of course we won't do that. As a matter of fact I think it's best that we "
"don't say anything to the elves at all."
msgstr ""
"Bien sûr que nous ne ferons pas ça. En fait, je crois que le mieux serait "
"qu'on n'en souffle pas un mot aux elfes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:88
msgid "Why d'ye say that?"
msgstr "Et pourquoi donc ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:93
msgid ""
"Well, suppose we do join up with the elves - assuming they will let us - and "
"we make a combined raid on the fortress, what will the orcs most likely do "
"when the ransom slips from their grasp?"
msgstr ""
"Hé bien, imaginons que nous nous alliions aux elfes - en supposant qu'ils "
"acceptent - et que nous lancions une attaque combinée sur la forteresse, "
"comment croyez-vous que les orcs réagiront en voyant qu'ils n'obtiendront "
"pas la rançon ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:98
msgid ""
"Kenning the way of orcs, belike they'd kill the princess, especially if it "
"seems the rescue ha' any chance of succeeding."
msgstr ""
"Connaissant les orcs, ils tueront sûrement la princesse, surtout si le raid "
"tourne à notre avantage."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:103
msgid ""
"Exactly. On the other hand, if we raided the fortress while the orcs were "
"talking ransom with the elves, the orcs might hesitate just long enough."
msgstr ""
"Exactement. D'un autre côté, si nous attaquons la forteresse par nous-mêmes "
"pendant que les elfes négocient la rançon avec les orcs, les orcs hésiteront "
"juste le temps qu'il nous faut."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:108
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hmmm...I think you've the right of it, lad. Most orcs being thicker than a "
"wood-knot, I'd lay odds on Rakshas giving strict orders that she not be "
"touched without his direct word on the matter."
msgstr ""
"Hummm... Je pense que tu as raison, mon ami. La plupart des orcs sont plus "
"bêtes qu'un bout de bois, je suis prêt à parier que Rakshas a donné des "
"instructions strictes pour qu'on ne touche pas à la princesse sans qu'il en "
"donne directement l'ordre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:113
msgid ""
"But it would be unwise to trust that the orcs will stay stupid forever. If "
"we do go ahead with this raid, we are going to have to be in and out like "
"lightning."
msgstr ""
"Néanmoins, je doute que les orcs restent stupides indéfiniment. Si nous "
"effectuons ce raid, nous allons devoir sortir la princesse de là en un rien "
"de temps."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:118
msgid ""
"My Shinsplitters will be invaluable for a job like this. They are fierce and "
"never give ground and will not stop attacking until either they or their "
"opponent lies dead. No fortress can stand long against them."
msgstr ""
"Mes Brisetibias seront d'une valeur inestimable pour ce type de mission. Ils "
"sont acharnés, ils ne se battent pas en retraite pas et ne cessent "
"d'attaquer qu'à leur mort ou à celle de leur adversaire. Aucune forteresse "
"ne leur résiste bien longtemps."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:123
msgid ""
"Ha ha, I like this plan. Once we get our hands on this little sorceress the "
"elves will be forced to do whatever we want them to."
msgstr ""
"Ha ha, que j'aime ce plan ! Une fois que nous aurons mis la main sur cette "
"petite sorcière, les elfes seront forcés de faire tout ce que nous voulons."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:128
msgid ""
"Remember, Ro'Arthian, we need willing allies rather than resentful lackeys "
"that would turn on us at the first reverse. If we rescue their princess, the "
"elves may yet choose not to help us, but that is a risk we'll have to take."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Arthian, rappelle-toi que nous voulons des alliés consentants, pas des "
"otages. Si nous délivrons leur princesse, les elfes pourront choisir de nous "
"aider ou pas, mais c'est un risque à prendre."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Elves are deeply honor-bound, especially in matters that touch their kin. If "
"we rescue the princess, I am certain the deed will not go without reward."
msgstr ""
"Les elfes sont très attachés à l'honneur, spécialement quand cela concerne "
"leurs proches. Si nous sauvons la princesse, je suis certain que notre "
"exploit sera récompensé."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:138
msgid ""
"And at the very least, the orcs will not be able to raise troops with ransom "
"money they don't have."
msgstr ""
"Et le meilleur dans tout ça, c'est que les orcs ne pourront pas lever plus "
"de troupes avec l'argent d'une rançon qu'ils n'ont pas."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:143
msgid "Pah...weak, soft humans. Have it your way if you must."
msgstr ""
"Peuh... humains faibles et tendres. Faites donc à votre manière, s'il le "
"faut."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:148
msgid ""
"So it shall be, Tallin, I'll hold the caves here while you and Stalrag's "
"Shinsplitters fare to Bitterhold. The orcs still haven't given up their "
"attack on our southern tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Alors le problème est réglé. Tallin, je resterai ici une fois de plus pour "
"tenir les grottes pendant que toi et les Brisetibias de Stalrag attaquez "
"Castel Amer. Les orcs n'ont toujours pas abandonné leurs attaques sur les "
"galeries sud."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:153
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then to arms, men! For Knalga and the princess!"
msgstr "Alors, aux armes, les gars ! Pour Knalga et pour la princesse !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/08a_Elvish_Princess.cfg:186
msgid "Rescue the Princess"
msgstr "Délivrer la princesse"

