msgstr "Bak'man"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1130
msgid "Halk"
msgstr "Halk"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1145
msgid "Hey! Look who's back!"
msgstr "Hé ! Regardez qui est revenu !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1152
msgid "And look, he brought his friends too!"
msgstr "Et devinez quoi, il a amené des copains !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1157
msgid "GRRRRRRR!"
msgstr "GRRRRRR !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1162
msgid "ROOOAAARRRR!!!"
msgstr "ROOOAAARRRR !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1167
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hurry, friends, let's set up camp!"
msgstr "Mes amis, dépêchons-nous d'installer le camp !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1172
msgid "Yeah, man! I knew we could count on you!"
msgstr "Ouais mec ! Je savais qu'on pouvait compter sur toi !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1177
msgid ""
"Hmmm, he must have smelled the scent of other drakes and gone to them to "
"convince them to help us."
msgstr ""
"Hmmm, il a dû sentir l'odeur d'autres dracans et il est parti les convaincre "
"de nous aider."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1182
msgid "Awww, what a darling!"
msgstr "Ohhh, qu'il est chou !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/10a_Stolen_Gold.cfg:1187
msgid "Tell that to the trolls."
