#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:8
msgid ""
"After breaking out of their encirclement, the party continued in pursuit of "
"the trolls."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir ouvert une brèche dans le cercle d'attaquants qui l'entourait, "
"le groupe repartit à la poursuite des trolls."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:12
msgid ""
"Following the bank of a river, they soon entered a valley. At the mouth of "
"the valley there loomed the massive orcish fortress of Angthurim."
msgstr ""
"En suivant les rives du fleuve, ils arrivèrent bientôt dans une vallée ; à "
"son entrée se dressait l'imposante citadelle orc d'Angthurim."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:41
msgid "Gore"
msgstr "Gore"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:59
msgid "Carron"
msgstr "Carron"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:71
msgid "Rash"
msgstr "Rash"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:83
msgid "Al'Mar"
msgstr "Al'Mar"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:95
msgid "Ha'Tang"
msgstr "Ha'Tang"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:252
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gods of Light! Look at that fortress. The castle Angthurim is even grimmer "
"than its reputation."
msgstr ""
"Dieux de la lumière ! Regardez cette forteresse. Le château Angthurim est "
"encore pire que sa réputation."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:263
msgid ""
"I was not idle in my captivity; I watched, and listened, and learned. The "
"hints I got from my guards' boastings and foul jests have been confirmed by "
"our scouts; Angthurim is the linchpin of their entire eastern flank. If we "
"could reduce it, their defense would be near to collapse."
msgstr ""
"Je ne suis pas resté inactif durant ma captivité. J'ai regardé, j'ai écouté "
"et j'ai appris. Ce que j'ai appris des vantardises de mes gardes et de leurs "
"stupides plaisanteries a été confirmé par nos éclaireurs ; Angthurim est "
"l'épine dorsale de tout leur flanc est. Toute leur défense pourrait "
"s'écrouler si nous pouvions le neutraliser."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:270
msgid ""
"Fitting. My gryphons tell me Angthurim is the keystone of their entire "
"eastern flank. If we can reduce it their defense will be near to collapse."
msgstr ""
"Ça se confirme. Mes griffons me disent qu'Angthurim est la pierre angulaire "
"de tout leur flanc est. Si nous pouvons le neutraliser, leur défense sera "
"sur le point de s'écrouler."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:278
msgid "Hey, look who is here!"
msgstr "Hé, regardez qui est là !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:283
msgid "Where is my gold!"
msgstr "Où est mon or !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:288
msgid "It's Rakshas!"
msgstr "C'est Rakshas !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:293
msgid "Right here, Master."
msgstr "Ici, maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:298
msgid ""
"Ahhhhh, very good, my loyal servant. You will be richly rewarded for this! "
"Tell me, what news do you have on that human vermin that has so persistently "
"evaded my clutches?"
msgstr ""
"Ahhhh, très bien, fidèle serviteur. Tu en seras grandement récompensé ! Dis-"
"moi, as-tu des nouvelles de la vermine humaine qui ne cesse de me glisser "
"entre les griffes ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:303
msgid ""
"We trapped him and his pitiful band of followers. By now they will have been "
"mashed to paste and fed to the whelps."
msgstr ""
"Nous l'avons piégé lui et ses pitoyables suiveurs. À l'heure qu'il est, ils "
"ne sont plus que de la pâtée pour louveteaux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:308
msgid "Hahahaha! Very g..."
msgstr "Ha ha ha ha ! Excell..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:313
msgid "RAKSHAS!!!"
msgstr "RAKSHAS !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:318
msgid ""
"What!? YOU! YOU ANNOYING, DISGUSTING LITTLE VERMIN! DON'T YOU KNOW HOW TO "
"DIE!?"
msgstr ""
"Quoi ?!? ENCORE TOI ! INSUPPORTABLE ET RÉPUGNANTE PETITE VERMINE ! NE PEUX-"
"TU DONC PAS MOURIR UNE BONNE FOIS POUR TOUTES !?!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:323
msgid ""
"Foul one, the only one who will be dying here is you and anyone who comes "
"between us. Stand and fight!"
msgstr ""
"Désolé l'ami, mais si quelqu'un doit mourir ici, ce sera toi, ainsi que "
"quiconque qui tentera de s'interposer. En garde !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:328
msgid ""
"Pah! I have better things to do then stamp out your insignificant life. "
"Generals, kill him and bring me his head!"
msgstr ""
"Peuh ! J'ai bien mieux à faire que de mettre fin à ta misérable existence. "
"Généraux, tuez-le et rapportez-moi sa tête !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:372
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Blast it. The coward has fled. Anita, your elves are good at moving quickly "
"through the forests. Do you think they can overtake and pin him down while "
"we deal with this fortress?"
msgstr ""
"Merde. La poule mouillée à foutu le camp. Anita, les elfes sont réputés pour "
"leur rapidité en forêt. Pensez-vous qu'ils pourront rattraper ce lâche et "
"lui couper la route ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:377
msgid "Hidel?"
msgstr "Hidel ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:382
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Easily, princess. We shall move unseen through the trees, overtake him, and "
"put an end to his flight."
msgstr ""
"Sans problème, princesse. Nous allons traverser les bois invisibles comme "
"des ombres, le rattraper et le coincer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:387
msgid ""
"Then do it. I shall stay with Tallin and... um... because he could use my "
"assistance."
msgstr ""
"Alors faites. Je resterai avec Tallin pour... hum... au cas où il aurait "
"besoin de moi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:392
msgid " *blushes slightly*"
msgstr " *rougit légèrement*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:397
msgid " *wink wink*"
msgstr " *clin d'œil entendu*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:402
msgid " *raises eyebrow* Very well, princess."
msgstr " *lève un sourcil* Il en sera fait selon vos désirs, princesse."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Blast it. The coward has fled. Quickly men, we must storm this fortress "
"before he can spend that gold."
msgstr ""
"Malédiction, le pleutre s'est enfui. Hâtons-nous, soldats, il faut raser "
"cette forteresse avant qu'il n'utilise cet or à mauvais escient."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:414
msgid "Aye! Down wi' the orcs!"
msgstr "Ouais ! À bas les orcs !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:421
msgid "Ro'Arthian, send a message to Hamel. Tell him it's time."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Arthian, envoyez un message à Hamel. Dites-lui que l'heure est venue."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:437
msgid "It's done."
msgstr "C'est fait."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:442
#, fuzzy
msgid "Very well. Forward! Victory or death!"
msgstr "En avant ! La victoire ou la mort !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:472
msgid "Come on boys, let's give it to 'em!"
msgstr "Allez les gars, donnons-leur une bonne raclée !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:536
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We have torn the heart from their eastern defenses. Now to settle scores "
"with Rakshas once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"C'est bon, le flanc oriental des orcs est éventré. Nous allons maintenant "
"régler nos comptes avec Rakshas une bonne fois pour toutes !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:552
msgid ""
"We have torn the heart from their eastern defenses. Now let us make haste to "
"rescue Hidel. I am uneasy for him; some of those bodyguards Rakshas keeps "
"are fell fighters."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons percé le cœur de leurs défenses orientales. Maintenant, il faut "
"sauver Hidel au plus vite. J'ai peur pour lui ; il y a de fameux combattants "
"parmi les gardes du corps de Rakshas."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:565
msgid "Move, you stupid orcs! I am trying to recruit here!"
msgstr ""
"Poussez-vous de là, espèces d'orcs stupides ! Je voudrais recruter ici !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:570
msgid "Suit yourself, you dumb troll!"
msgstr "Fais comme chez toi, troll débile !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/11a_Eastern_Flank.cfg:575
msgid ""
"Awww, aren't they the most loving, sharing bunch of orcs you have ever seen?"
msgstr ""
"Ahhh, ne sont-ils pas les orcs les plus adorables, les plus charitables "
"qu'on ait jamais vus ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:4
msgid "Get the Gold"
msgstr "Récupérer l'or"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:9
msgid ""
"After reducing Castle Angthurim, the party set off after Rakshas, hoping "
"that Hidel's elves had been able to hold him."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir conquis Château Angthurim, le groupe partit à la suite de "
"Rakshas, espérant que les elfes d'Hidel aient été capables de le retenir."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Orcs are heavy-footed creatures; Rakshas's trail was readily followed. But "
"an ominous silence, broken only by the cawing of ravens, brooded over the "
"road he had taken."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs ont le pas lourd ; la piste de Rakshas fut facile à suivre. Mais un "
"silence de mauvais augure, brisé seulement par le croassement des corbeaux, "
"régnait sur le chemin qu'il empruntait."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Soon they encountered the wrack of a great battle. Bodies of elves and orcs "
"lay everywhere. Broken weapons and smashed armor were strewn about in "
"profusion. Elvish arrows and orcish crossbow bolts bristled from the nearby "
"trees. The ground was splotched red with blood."
msgstr ""
"Ils débouchèrent rapidement sur les vestiges d'une grande bataille. Des "
"corps d'elfes et d'orcs gisaient partout. Des armes brisées et des armures "
"défoncées étaient éparpillées de tous côtés. Les arbres alentour étaient "
"criblés de flèches elfes et de carreaux d'arbalète orcs. La terre était "
"rouge de sang."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:22
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They paused for scant minutes to bind the wounds of a few surving elves and "
"leave them a small guard. Then they pressed onward to rescue Hidel - and "
"they found him."
msgstr ""
"Ils s'arrêtèrent à peine quelques minutes pour bander les blessures des "
"quelques elfes survivants et leur laissèrent quelques gardes. Ils se "
"hâtèrent ensuite pour secourir Hidel, et ils le trouvèrent."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Scattered around Hidel were the bodies of at least three orcish warlords, "
"and nearly a score of grunts, warriors and crossbowmen. His weapons were "
"notched and broken; his armor dented and smashed. It was clear to all that "
"his fall had been an epic of valor and glory, worthy to be remembered in the "
"songs of all the kindred races until the end of days."
msgstr ""
"Autour d'Hidel étaient éparpillés les corps d'au moins trois seigneurs de "
"guerre orcs, d'une escouade de grognards orcs, des guerriers et des "
"arbalétriers. Ses armes étaient endommagées ou brisées ; son armure était "
"bosselée et défoncée. Tous virent qu'il s'était défendu avec une ardeur "
"héroïque et que sa chute même lui apporterait une gloire dont tous se "
"souviendraient."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:30
msgid ""
"With tears streaming down her face, Anita approached the fallen hero and "
"cradled his head in her lap. As she stroked his face, his eyes fluttered "
"open."
msgstr ""
"En larmes, Anita s'approcha du héros tombé et mit délicatement sa tête sur "
"ses genoux. Alors qu'elle caressait son visage, ses paupières battirent "
"faiblement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:34
msgid ""
"I am sorry, princess... We held him for... as long as we could... but his "
"bodyguards... were... just too many and powerful... And then... the "
"orcish... reinforcements arrived...."
msgstr ""
"Je suis désolé, princesse... Nous les avons retenus... aussi longtemps que "
"possible... mais ses gardes du corps... étaient... simplement trop "
"nombreux... et trop forts... Et puis... les orcs... sont arrivés en "
"renfort..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Her face streaked with tears, Anita gazed imploringly at Father Marcus and "
"Sister Theta. They simply sighed and shook their heads. It was too late to "
"save Hidel. In a broken voice Anita addressed him:"
msgstr ""
"Le visage en pleurs, Anita implora du regard Père Marcus et Sœur Theta. Ils "
"se contentèrent de soupirer et hochèrent doucement la tête. Il était trop "
"tard pour sauver Hidel. Anita leur parla d'une voix brisée :"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:43
msgid "Hidel, I am sorry. I have sent you to your death, and I grieve."
msgstr "Je regrette, Hidel. Je regrette tant de t'avoir envoyé à la mort."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:48
msgid ""
"...Don't tax yourself... princess.... I have died.... a warrior's death.... "
"you should be proud...."
msgstr ""
"...Ne vous affligez pas... princesse... Je suis tombé... en guerrier... "
"soyez-en fière..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:53
msgid ""
"...But.... there is.... one thing.... we.... could do. We .... managed "
"to.... recover the gold....Sisal... took it and.... retreated south...."
msgstr ""
"... Mais... il y a une chose... que... nous pourrions faire... Nous avons "
"réussi... à... récupérer l'or... Sisal... l'a pris et... a fait retraite "
"vers le sud..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:58
msgid ""
"I held out as.... long as.... I could.... but they..... defeated us.... "
"Rakshas went.... east and the.... rest.... went.... after.... Sisal..."
msgstr ""
"J'ai lutté... autant que... j'ai pu... mais ils nous... ont vaincu... "
"Rakshas est allé... à l'est... et les autres... sont partis... à la suite de "
"Sisal..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:63
msgid ""
"Now... uphold the honour... of the Northern... Elves.... recover.... the "
"gold.... slay this monster.... and bring peace and... prosperity.... back to "
"the... Northlands... Tallin?"
msgstr ""
"À présent... défendez l'honneur... des elfes... du nord... retrouvez l'or... "
"tuez ce monstre... et ramenez la paix... et la prospérité aux Royaumes du "
"Nord... Tallin ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:68
msgid ""
"At Hidel's call Tallin approached and kelt beside Hidel, bowing his head in "
"respect."
msgstr ""
"À l'appel d'Hidel, Tallin s'approcha et s'agenouilla à ses côtés, inclinant "
"la tête avec respect."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:72
msgid "At your service, sir."
msgstr "À votre service, Monseigneur."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:77
msgid ""
"Anita has been... my charge ever... since she was born.... I now return... "
"to the earth... from which.... I sprang... Please take care... of her."
msgstr ""
"Anita est sous... ma protection depuis... sa naissance... Je retourne "
"maintenant... à la terre... d'où je viens... Je vous en prie... prenez soin "
"d'elle."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:82
msgid ""
"Rest assured sir, I will place myself between Anita and any ill that "
"strength or love may counter."
msgstr ""
"Reposez en paix, Monseigneur, ma force et mon amour seront un rempart pour "
"Anita."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:87
msgid ""
"Thank you... Tallin.... Now I may rest... in... peace.... May you.... be "
"victorious..."
msgstr ""
"Merci... Tallin... Je vais enfin pouvoir reposer... en... paix... Puisses-tu "
"triompher..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:92
msgid ""
"With these words Hidel closed his eyes and breathed his last. As Anita wept "
"with Hidel's head in her lap, Tallin approached her, hesitating, and then "
"wrapped her gently in his arms."
msgstr ""
"À ces mots, Hidel ferma les yeux et poussa son dernier soupir. Comme Anita "
"pleurait sur la tête d'Hidel dans son giron, Tallin s'approcha d'elle, "
"hésitant et l'entoura gentiment de ses bras."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:96
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Sobbing against Tallin's chest, Anita told him of the many ways Hidel had "
"cherished and warded her since the hour of her birth. How he had comforted "
"her childhood hurts; how in later years, he had guided her in the green "
"paths of the forest, and taught her the deep mysteries of Elven-kind."
msgstr ""
"Pleurant contre la poitrine de Tallin, Anita lui raconta les mille façons "
"dont Hidel l'avait chérie et protégée depuis l'heure de sa naissance ; "
"comment il l'avait consolée des soucis de l'enfance ; comment, ces dernières "
"années, il l'avait guidé sur les chemins verdoyants des forêts et lui avait "
"enseigné les mystères les mieux gardés des elfes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:100
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A torrent of childhood memories and the depth of her grief left her unable "
"to speak. She and Tallin sat together silently holding each-other for some "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Le flot de ses souvenir d'enfance et la profondeur de son chagrin "
"l'empêchèrent d'en dire plus. Tallin et elle s'assirent ensemble "
"silencieusement, enlacés."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:104
msgid ""
"As Tallin comforted Anita, the rest of the party spread out and rallied the "
"scattered elves, and tending to the wounded. This being done, they once "
"again came before Tallin and Anita."
msgstr ""
"Alors que Tallin réconfortait Anita, le reste du groupe allèrent trouver les "
"survivant elfes éparpillés pour les soigner. Quand ce fut fait, ils "
"revinrent auprès d'eux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:108
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Princess...it is a hard thing, I know, but you must put your grief behind "
"you. Or at least, put it aside for a little while. We must go quickly to the "
"aid of Sisal and recover our gold."
msgstr ""
"Princesse... je sais que c'est difficile, mais vous devez oublier votre "
"chagrin. Ou au moins pendant un petit moment.  Nous devons vite aller aider "
"Sisal et récupérer notre or."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:113
msgid ""
"Forge your sorrow into rage, girl, and visit it on the slayers of your "
"kinsmen. Teach them what happens to those who make an enemy of an elf."
msgstr ""
"Transformez votre peine en colère, petite fille, et déversez-là sur les "
"assassins de votre semblable. Apprenez-leur ce qui arrive à ceux qui "
"s'attaquent aux elfes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:118
msgid ""
"At these words, Anita arose and wiped away her tears. She took command of "
"the surviving elvish forces, for all knew she was a princess of high rank "
"and looked to Hidel's ward as their leader by right. Scarcely a face among "
"them was less grim than her own as they took arms and started down Rakshas's "
"back-trail."
msgstr ""
"À ces mots, Anita se leva et s'essuya les yeux. Elle pris le commandement "
"des elfes survivants qui tous savaient qu'elle était une princesse de haut "
"rang et qu'elle avait le droit de remplacer Hidel. Rarement on vit un visage "
"aussi terrible que le sien alors qu'elle prenait les armes et qu'elle "
"partait à la chasse de Raksas."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:122
msgid ""
"Moments later a gryphon swooped down from overhead and reported battle in a "
"forest just a few leagues south of their position. The remainder of the "
"elvish forces had been espied fighting a desperate battle with the orcs."
msgstr ""
"Quelques instants plus tard, un griffon, surgi du ciel, leur dit qu'il y "
"avait une bataille dans la forêt qui était à peine à quelques lieues au sud "
"d'eux. Les elfes survivants avaient été aperçus en train de lutter contre "
"les orcs avec la violence du désespoir."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:126
msgid ""
"It seemed to the gryphon that the elves were sore beset. The party quickly "
"turned south and plunged into the forest."
msgstr ""
"Le griffon semblait dire que les elfes étaient sévèrement mis à l'épreuve. "
"Le groupe s'orienta rapidement vers le sud et plongea dans la forêt."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:96
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:51
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:171
msgid "Ha'Tuil"
msgstr "Ha'Tuil"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:126
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:65
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:188
msgid "Ar'Muff"
msgstr "Ar'Muff"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:705
msgid ""
"After making haste through the forest for most of a watch, the party arrived "
"at the battle scene."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir traversé à toute allure la forêt, le groupe arriva sur le lieu "
"de la bataille."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:711
msgid "Sisal, how do you fare?"
msgstr "Sisal, comment ça va ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:716
msgid "Princess! You are here! How fares Hidel?"
msgstr "Princesse ! Vous êtes ici ! Comment va Hidel ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:721
msgid " *sheds a tear*"
msgstr " *verse une larme*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:726
msgid "Hidel...died a hero's death, one worthy to be sung forever."
msgstr "Hidel... est mort en héros, son nom sera chanté pour toujours."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:731
msgid ""
"The dung-spawned bastards! Verily, Tallin, had it not been for Hidel we "
"would all be dead and Rakshas would be gleefully counting his gold."
msgstr ""
"Quelle bande de roulures de purin ! En vérité, Tallin, nous serions tous "
"morts sans Hidel, et Rakshas serait en train de compter joyeusement son or."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:736
msgid ""
"Hidel and a handful of elves held off the orcs for more then an hour. That "
"was enough time for us to make off with the gold and rally here at these "
"ruins."
msgstr ""
"Hidel et une poignée d'elfes ont résisté aux orcs pendant plus d'une heure. "
"Cela a été suffisant pour mettre l'or à l'abri et nous retrouver dans ces "
"ruines."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:741
msgid "So you have the gold?"
msgstr "Donc tu as l'or ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:746
msgid ""
"We have the gold, and now we shall have the blood of these orcs! IN HIDEL'S "
"NAME!"
msgstr ""
"Nous avons l'or. Et maintenant, allons répandre le sang de ces orcs ! EN "
"SOUVENIR D'HIDEL !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:751
msgid ""
"Grrr, Ha'Tuil has never failed in his mission. I will soon lay your severed "
"heads at the feet of the Master!"
msgstr ""
"Grrr, Ha'Tuil n'a jamais failli à ses missions. Je vais bientôt expédier "
"toutes vos têtes aux pieds du maître !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:756
msgid ""
"You will eat cold steel and whimper your way to hell, foul wretch of an orc!"
msgstr ""
"On va vous faire bouffer notre acier et vous allez en baver jusqu'en enfer, "
"misérables orcs puants !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:762
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:787
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:812
msgid "Defeat the orcs"
msgstr "Vaincre les orcs"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:846
msgid "Argh! I have failed!"
msgstr "Non ! J'ai échoué."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:851
msgid ""
"Cheer up -- you won't have to live with your failure for long...*snicker*"
msgstr ""
"Fais risette, tu n'auras pas longtemps à vivre avec cet échec sur le cœur..."
"*ricanement*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:869
msgid "Ahhhh! Farewell, friends. I now go to join Hidel."
msgstr "Ahhhh ! Adieu mes amis. Je m'en vais à présent rejoindre Hidel."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:874
msgid "Sisal! Noooo!"
msgstr "Sisal ! Noooon !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:879
msgid "Haha! We got the gold now!"
msgstr "Haha ! C'est nous qui avons l'or maintenant !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:884
msgid ""
"Hahaha! Mission accomplished, men! Now let's crush the rest of this scum and "
"report back to the Master."
msgstr ""
"Hahaha ! Mission accomplie, les gars ! Maintenant, allons écraser les autres "
"raclures et allons faire notre rapport au Maître."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:889
msgid ""
"I don't think so, you bastard orcs! That gold belongs to us. Besides, we now "
"have a few scores to settle with you. Take them, troops - I want no orc left "
"alive!"
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez vous gratter, enflure d'orcs ! Cet or est à nous. Et pis, il est "
"temps de régler quelques comptes. À l'assaut, soldats ! Massacrez-les tous !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/12a_Get_the_Gold.cfg:903
msgid ""
"Thanks to Hidel and the elves, we have recovered our gold. Now let's run "
"down Rakshas and settle up with him once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons retrouvé notre or grâce à Hidel et aux elfes. Lançons-nous à la "
"poursuite de Rakshas dès maintenant, et finissons-en avec lui une bonne fois "
"pour toute."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:4
msgid "Showdown"
msgstr "Confrontation"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The party once again took up Raksha's trail. They soon received a report "
"from a scouting gryphon that in an enormous fortress a few leagues west from "
"them, Rakshas was assembling a massive orcish force, clearly intending to "
"crush their revolt once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Le groupe repartit une fois de plus les traces de Rakshas. Ils reçurent "
"bientôt le rapport d'un griffon parti en éclaireur qui affirmait qu'une "
"énorme forteresse, à quelques lieues à l'ouest de leur position, servait de "
"point de ralliement à une armée d'orcs colossale, clairement destinée à "
"écraser leur révolte une bonne fois pour toute. "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:13
msgid ""
"The gryphon further reported that a few more leagues west was a large force "
"of dwarvish veterans, advancing steadily on the orcish fortress."
msgstr ""
"Le griffon signala aussi une importante force naine, quelques lieues encore "
"plus à l'ouest , qui fonçait tout droit sur la citadelle orc."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Battle plans were quickly made; the party split into three groups. Two of "
"the groups immediately set off northwest and southwest respectively while "
"the third group rested for an hour and then set off directly west."
msgstr ""
"Des plans de bataille furent rapidement établis et le groupe se divisa en "
"trois armées. Deux partirent immédiatement, l'une vers le nord-ouest, "
"l'autre vers le sud-ouest, tandis que la troisième armée se reposa une heure "
"puis mit le cap sur l'ouest."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The idea was to completely surround Rakshas on all sides, cutting off any "
"chance of escape or reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"Le but était d'encercler complètement Rakshas, pour lui ôter toute "
"possibilité de retraite ou de renforts."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:156
msgid "Calter"
msgstr "Calter"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:186
msgid "Halter"
msgstr "Halter"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:574
msgid ""
"The group that went to the north was led by Ro'Arthian and was composed of "
"trolls, orges and some selected mages."
msgstr ""
"L'armée qui se dirigea vers le nord était menée par Ro'Arthian et était "
"composée de trolls, d'ogres et de mages soigneusement choisis."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:582
msgid ""
"The group that went to the north was led by Krash and his drake friends."
msgstr "L'armée partie vers le nord était menée par Krash et ses amis dracans."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:596
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Anita and the remaining elves, eager to avenge Hidel, went south, while "
"Tallin himself led the western group."
msgstr ""
"Anita et le reste de l'armée elfe, avides de vengeance depuis la mort de "
"Hidel, se dirigèrent vers le sud, pendant que Tallin lui-même commandait la "
"division ouest."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:604
msgid ""
"Ro'Arthian's brother, Ro'Sothian went south with another crew of trolls, "
"ogres and mages. Tallin himself led the western group."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Sothian, le frère de Ro'Arthian, partit au sud avec une autre troupe de "
"trolls, d'ogres et de mages. Tallin lui-même prit le commandement de la "
"division ouest."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:612
msgid "A few short hours later all the groups converged on the fortress."
msgstr ""
"Au bout de quelques petites heures, toutes les armées convergèrent vers la "
"citadelle."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:756
msgid ""
"Rakshas! You have evaded me for the last time. Now come out and die like a "
"man!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:761
msgid "What the...? How did he get here?"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que... ? Comment a-t-il pu arriver jusqu'ici ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:772
msgid ""
"We have crushed and scattered your entire eastern flank, and now it's your "
"turn!"
msgstr ""
"Nous avons pulvérisé tout ton flanc oriental, et maintenant c'est ton tour !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:777
msgid ""
"You slimy little elf! So you have joined hands with these humans, have you? "
"Very well, both of you shall soon be dead!"
msgstr ""
"Petit avorton d'elfe ! Ainsi, tu te bats avec ces humains, n'est-ce pas ? "
"Très bien, vous serez bientôt morts, tous les deux !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Good luck, you monster. You are cut off and surrounded. We shall kill you "
"and feed your carcass to the vultures and wild beasts."
msgstr ""
"Bonne chance, monstre. Tu es isolé et encerclé. Bientôt nous te tuerons et "
"jetterons ton cadavre aux vautours et aux bêtes sauvages."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:787
msgid ""
"Hahahahah! You fools, do you not see that you are right in the heart of "
"orcish territory, surrounded yourselves! Why, at this very moment my entire "
"western army is marching this way. They will soon be here and will scatter "
"your forces like straw!"
msgstr ""
"Hahahaha ! Bande d'idiots, ne voyez-vous pas que vous êtes en plein "
"territoire orc, que vous êtes vous-mêmes encerclés ! D'ailleurs, en ce "
"moment même mon armée occidentale au complet avance vers ce château. Ils "
"seront bientôt là et vous briseront comme un fétu de paille !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:794
msgid ""
"We have crushed and scattered your entire eastern flank, buddy, and now it's "
"your turn!"
msgstr ""
"Nous avons écrasé et réduit en poussière tout ton flanc est, mon pote, et "
"c'est à ton tour d'y passer maintenant !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:799
msgid ""
"Argh, you frustrating little vermin! I am going to pluck your eyeballs out "
"and..."
msgstr ""
"Argh, petite vermine enrageante ! Je vais vous arracher les yeux et "
"ensuite..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:804
msgid "We don't have any eyeballs, you idiot!"
msgstr "On n'a plus d'yeux, pauvre abruti !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:809
msgid ""
"PAH! You fools, know that you shall soon be outnumbered and surrounded. At "
"this very moment my entire western army is marching this way. They will soon "
"be here and will scatter your puny forces like straw!"
msgstr ""
"Peuh ! Pauvres fous, sachez que vous serez bientôt encerclés et engloutis "
"sous le nombre. En ce moment même, mon armée occidentale au complet s'avance "
"dans notre direction. Ils seront bientôt là et briseront vos faibles troupes "
"comme un fétu de paille."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:883
msgid "Will they, now?"
msgstr "T'en es sûr ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:888
msgid "WHAT!?!?!"
msgstr "QUOI !?!?!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:893
msgid ""
"Your western army has been slaughtered, Rakshas, and YOU will soon join them!"
msgstr ""
"Toute ton armée occidentale a été réduite en bouillie, Rakshas, et c'est TOI "
"qui vas aller les rejoindre dans l'au-delà de ce pas !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:898
msgid "But... but... how can this be?"
msgstr "Mais... mais... comment est-ce possible ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:903
msgid "It's called 'The End', foul orc. Forward! FOR KNALGA!!!"
msgstr "Ça s'appelle « La Fin », crétin d'orc. En avant, POUR KNALGA !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:908
msgid "FOR FRIENDSHIP!!!"
msgstr "POUR L'AMITIÉ !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:913
msgid "FOR PEACE!!!"
msgstr "POUR LA PAIX !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:918
msgid "FOR FUN!"
msgstr "POUR L'ÉCLATE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:923
msgid "FOR HIDEL!!!"
msgstr "POUR HIDEL !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:929
msgid "FOR DWARVEN DOORS!!!"
msgstr "POUR LES PORTES DES NAINS !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:934
msgid "FOR THE NORTH! FALL ON THEM, MEN!!!"
msgstr "POUR LE NORD ! CHARGEZ !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1020
msgid ""
"At last! Rakshas has been slain, and the orcish host has been crushed. Peace "
"and prosperity will come to the Northlands once again!"
msgstr ""
"Enfin ! Rakshas est mort et ses cohortes orcs ont été exterminées. La paix "
"et la prospérité vont revenir sur les Terres du Nord !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1025
msgid ""
"At these words all the allied forces gave out a combined and thunderous "
"cheer. Their long ordeal was finally over."
msgstr ""
"À ces mots, tous les alliés poussèrent un cri retentissant. Leur odyssée "
"était enfin terminée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1031
msgid " *small voice lost in the uproar* Awww, is it over already?"
msgstr ""
" *petite voix perdue dans le tumulte des clameurs* Ohhh, c'est déjà fini ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"Die, you murderous beast! No longer shall you terrorize the people of the "
"North."
msgstr ""
"Meurs, bête immonde ! Plus jamais tu ne terroriseras les peuples du Nord."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1051
msgid "Learn the fate of one who offends the Dwarves of Knalga."
msgstr "Vois ce qu'il en coûte d'offenser les nains de Knalga."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1056
msgid "Or the elves of the Northern Forests."
msgstr "Ou le peuple des Forêts du Nord."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1067
msgid "Or the humans of Dwarven Doors."
msgstr "Ou le peuple des Portes des Nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1072
msgid ""
" *gurggle* No!... this.... cannot.... be... happening.... to.... me....."
msgstr ""
" *d'une voix noyée dans le sang* Non !... ça... ne... peut... pas... "
"m'arriver... pas... à... moi......"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1077
msgid "Such were the last words of of Rakshas the great!"
msgstr "C'étaient les derniers mots de Rakshas le Grand !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:660
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:700
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:788
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1095
msgid "Argh!"
msgstr "Argh !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1100
msgid ""
"Hamel! Blast it, without the dwarves to hold the western flank we are as "
"good as defeated."
msgstr ""
"Hamel ! Sacrebleu, sans les nains pour tenir le flanc ouest, c'est comme si "
"nous avions déjà perdu."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1109
msgid "Sweet gods, look at all those orcs pouring out of that fortress."
msgstr ""
"Damnation, regardez-moi tous ces orcs qui sortent en masse de la forteresse !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1114
msgid "Aye, and not just any orcs either, those are all hardened veterans!"
msgstr "Ouaip, et pas n'importe quels orcs, que des vétérans endurcis !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1119
msgid ""
"Yeah. Obviously this is going to take some time. If necessary we can sit "
"tight in our fortifications and siege them until they starve!"
msgstr ""
"Ouais. C'est clair que ça risque de durer un bon bout de temps. Si c'est "
"nécessaire, nous pouvons construire des fortifications et les assiéger "
"jusqu'à ce qu'ils meurent de faim !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1137
msgid "Ahhhh! Farewell friends. I now go to join Hidel."
msgstr "Ahhhh ! Adieu mes amis. Je m'en vais à présent rejoindre Hidel."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/13a_Showdown.cfg:1142
msgid "Sisal! Noooo! Not you too!"
msgstr "Sisal ! Noooon ! Pas toi aussi !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:4
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "Épilogue"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:8
msgid ""
"The dead and wounded being cared for, and after the party had wound down, "
"everyone gathered in the conquered castle to decide on their course of "
"action."
msgstr ""
"On enterra les morts et on s'occupa des blessés. Après la dispersion du "
"détachement, tout le monde se rassembla dans la forteresse conquise pour "
"décider de la suite des évènements."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:238
msgid ""
"So, Rakshas has been defeated and all the armies that he had gathered have "
"been crushed. This relieves a blight on our land - but if we do not address "
"the causes of the blight, we could be in for trouble later."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi, Rakshas est vaincu et toutes les armées orcs qu'il avait levées ont "
"été anéanties. Notre terre est débarrassée de ce fléau, mais nous pourrions "
"le regretter plus tard si nous n'en recherchons pas les causes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:243
#, fuzzy
msgid "How is that, Tallin?"
msgstr "Comment ça, Tallin ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Rakshas was but a symptom. The ill is the nature of the orcs themselves."
msgstr ""
"Rakshas n'était que le symptôme d'un mal plus grand provenant de la nature "
"même des orcs."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:253
msgid ""
"The orcs are exceedingly numerous and warlike. While they squabble among "
"themselves, their warlike nature turns upon itself and they are no threat; "
"but when a strong warlord like Rakshas arises among them, their battle-lust "
"becomes a plague upon their neighbors."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs sont incroyablement nombreux et batailleurs. Tant qu'ils se "
"chamaillent entre eux, leur nature guerrière ne fait du mal qu'à eux et ils "
"ne représentent pas une menace ; mais quand un puissant seigneur de guerre "
"comme Rakshas apparaît parmi eux, leur rage meurtrière devient une vraie "
"plaie pour leurs voisins."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:264
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Our challenge is to ensure that the orcs do not unite under one strong, "
"warlike leader in the future."
msgstr ""
"Notre combat sera de nous assurer que les orcs ne s'unissent plus derrière "
"un chef puissant et belliqueux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:279
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr "Exactement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:284
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Aye. And we dinna just want to keep the orcs from ruling the Northlands; we "
"want to make the Northlands a safe place for all the kindred races to trade, "
"travel and live in peace. We must also ensure that no isolated bands of "
"orcs, trolls, ogres or any other creatures will be roving around praying on "
"innocent people."
msgstr ""
"Ouais. Et les orcs ne doivent plus régner sur les Terres du Nord. Il faut "
"qu'elles deviennent un lieu sûr où les gens pourront commercer, voyager et "
"vivre en paix. Il faut aussi éviter que des innocents soient attaqués par "
"des bandes isolées d'orcs, de trolls, d'ogres ou d'autres créatures errantes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:289
msgid "A worthy and difficult task. Does anybody have any ideas?"
msgstr ""
"C'est un travail difficile, mais ça en vaut la peine. Quelqu'un aurait-il "
"une idée ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:294
msgid "I do have a suggestion."
msgstr "Moi, j'ai bien une suggestion."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:299
msgid ""
"The orcs are too hardy and fast-breeding to be exterminated, even if we "
"could bring ourselves to stomach an attempt at slaughtering them all. "
"Therefore, we must find a way to make them part of our solution."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs ont le cuir trop dur et se multiplient trop vite pour pouvoir être "
"exterminés, même si vous trouvez les tripes de les massacrer tous un jour. "
"Nous devons donc trouver un moyen de faire avec."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:304
msgid ""
"I propose is the creation of a neutral council of warders, composed of "
"humans, dwarves, elves, drakes, trolls or anyone else who wishes to join, no "
"mater what race they come from - even orcs."
msgstr ""
"Je propose donc la création d'une assemblée impartiale de sentinelles, "
"regroupant humains, nains, elfes, dracans, trolls ou tout autre race "
"souhaitant nous rejoindre, quelle qu'elle soit, même des orcs."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:309
msgid ""
"This body would not claim sovereignty over any peoples or lands, but exist "
"only to suppress warfare and raiding in the lands south and east of the "
"Great Ocean, north of Wesnoth and west of the Elvish Forests."
msgstr ""
"Cet organe n'aurait de souveraineté sur aucune terre, peuple ou territoire "
"et n'aurait pas d'autre finalité que de mettre fin à la guerre et aux raids "
"sur les terres qui s'étendent au sud et à l'est du Grand Océan, au nord de "
"Wesnoth et à l'ouest des forêts elfes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:314
msgid ""
"The first task of the warders would be to go to go to each orcish tribe and "
"make a treaty with them that they will not be attacked if they refrain from "
"attacking others."
msgstr ""
"La première tâche des sentinelles serait d'aller dans chaque tribu orc pour "
"établir un pacte de non-agression mutuelle."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:319
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The orcs have just experienced a crushing defeat; it shouldn't be too hard "
"to get them to agree. In the future, if they should renege on their "
"treaties, and threaten the peace and prosperity of the North, then the army "
"maintained by the warders would crush them."
msgstr ""
"Les orcs viennent de subir une défaite écrasante ; il ne devrait donc pas "
"être trop difficile de leur faire accepter cet accord. Ensuite, s'ils "
"devaient revenir sur leur promesse et menacer la paix et la prospérité du "
"Nord, alors l'armée entretenue par les sentinelles irait les écraser."

# Damien : la forme interrogative, nuancée "Shall" est transcrite en français par "je propose".
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:324
msgid ""
"That is the basic outline of my proposal. Shall the Council of Warders "
"declare itself?"
msgstr ""
"Voilà les grandes lignes de ma proposition. C'est pourquoi je propose la "
"constitution d'un Conseil des Sentinelles."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:329
msgid ""
"Hearing the words of the wise mage, the whole assembly erupted with cries of "
"approval."
msgstr ""
"Les paroles du sage magicien soulevèrent un enthousiasme exubérant dans "
"l'assemblée entière."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:335
msgid "Fitting!"
msgstr "Bonne idée !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:341
msgid "Great!"
msgstr "Fantastique !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:346
msgid "Smart!"
msgstr "Astucieux !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:351
msgid "Sounds like fun."
msgstr "Ça me plaît !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Rising to his feet, Hamel raised his hands and waited for the clamor to die "
"down."
msgstr ""
"Se dressant sur ses pieds, Hamel leva les mains et attendit que la clameur "
"retombe."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Over time, Tallin has proved himself to be a wise, courageous and capable "
"leader. He is respected by humans, elves and dwarves alike. I therefore "
"propose that Tallin be made the first head of the Council of Warders."
msgstr ""
"Au fil du temps, Tallin a prouvé qu'il était un chef sage, courageux et "
"compétent. Il a gagné le respect des humains, des elfes et des nains. Je "
"propose donc que Tallin soit désigné à la tête de cette nouvelle "
"organisation."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Once again, all assembled erupted into thunderous approval. The tumult "
"lasted for some time and at long last Tallin rose to his feet and held up "
"his hands for quiet."
msgstr ""
"Une fois de plus, il y eut un tonnerre d'approbations. Le tumulte dura un "
"moment, jusqu'à ce qu'enfin Tallin se lève et réclame le silence en levant "
"les mains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:373
msgid ""
"I thank everyone for the love and honor bestowed upon me. In honor of that "
"love I accept this responsibility."
msgstr ""
"Je remercie tout le monde pour l'amour et l'honneur que vous m'accordez. En "
"l'honneur de cet amour, j'accepte cette responsabilité."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:378
msgid ""
"No one leader will make the Warders a success; we will need the help of all "
"of you."
msgstr ""
"Aucun chef ne fera le succès de ce conseil ; nous aurons besoin de l'aide de "
"chacun."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:383
msgid ""
"Father Marcus, this whole plan is your idea. Would you and your wife be "
"willing to stand by my side and support me?"
msgstr ""
"Père Marcus, cette proposition est la tienne. Seriez-vous d'accord, ta femme "
"et toi, pour rester à mes côtés et me soutenir ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:388
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gladly, Tallin. We will stand with the Warders till the end of days if need "
"be."
msgstr ""
"Avec joie, Tallin. Nous nous tiendrons aux côtés des Sentinelles jusqu'à la "
"fin des temps si besoin est."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:399
msgid "Stalrag?"
msgstr "Stalrag ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:404
msgid "I am yours to command, my lord Tallin."
msgstr "Je suis à vos ordres, Seigneur Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:409
msgid " 'Lord' Oh no!"
msgstr "Oh non, pas de « Monseigneur » !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:414
#, fuzzy
msgid " *giggle* Better get used to it."
msgstr "Hé hé, tu ferais bien de t'y habituer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:419
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You have led myself and the Shinsplitters wisely. We will uphold the Council "
"of Warders."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez conduit les Brise-Tibias et moi-même avec sagesse. Nous "
"soutiendrons les Conseils des Sentinelles. "

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:432
msgid "Camerin?"
msgstr "Camerin ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:437
msgid ""
"Heck yeah! It has been a total blast being with you. I wouldn't even think "
"of leaving now!"
msgstr ""
"Un peu mon neveu ! C'était complètement l'éclate tout le temps qu'j'étais "
"avec toi ! Il m'viendrait même pas à l'esprit d'partir maintenant !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:450
msgid "Elenia?"
msgstr "Elenia ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:455
msgid ""
"Tallin, as you know, I have been separated from my race and kinsmen - well, "
"except Anita - for many years now. I wish to go back to the elvish forests "
"and live among my kinsmen again. Perhaps I will return someday."
msgstr ""
"Tallin, comme vous le savez déjà, j'ai été séparé de ma race et de ma "
"famille - enfin, sauf d'Anita - pendant de nombreuses années. J'aimerais "
"rejoindre les forêts elfes et vivre à nouveau parmi les miens. Je reviendrai "
"peut-être un jour."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:466
msgid ""
"Knowing you and your spirit of adventure, Elenia, I am certain that you are "
"gonna be back sooner or later."
msgstr ""
"Connaissant votre goût pour l'aventure, Elenia, je suis certain que vous "
"reviendrez tôt ou tard."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:471
msgid " *smiles* It is not unlikely..."
msgstr " *sourire* C'est probable..."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:478
msgid ""
"You have been a valuable ally and a great friend, Elenia. Go with our "
"blessing, and convey to the Elves our intentions and the hope of peace."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez été une alliée de grande valeur et une merveilleuse amie, Elenia. "
"Allez avec notre bénédiction, et informez les elfes de nos intentions et de "
"nos espoirs de paix."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:483
msgid "Thank you Tallin."
msgstr "Merci Tallin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:497
msgid "Krash?"
msgstr "Krash ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:502
msgid ""
"I am sorry, Tallin but me and my friends had better be getting back to our "
"people."
msgstr ""
"Je regrette, Tallin, mais il vaut mieux que mes amis et moi retournions chez "
"les nôtres."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:507
msgid ""
"No need to apologize, Krash, for you and the valiant drakes of your band "
"have been of invaluable help to us. The entire Northlands are in your debt."
msgstr ""
"Pas besoin de t'excuser, Krash, toi et les amis dracans de ta bande avez été "
"d'une aide inestimable. L'ensemble des Terres du Nord vous est redevable."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:512
msgid ""
"As you said once before Tallin, let not talk of debts come between us. I "
"will spread the word among my people and if anyone wishes to join your "
"Council they will be free to. In addition to gaining the respect of the "
"elves and the dwarves you have also earned the respect of the drakes. I am "
"sure many will come to join your cause."
msgstr ""
"Comme tu l'as dit autrefois, Tallin, il n'est pas question de dettes entre "
"nous. Je répandrai la nouvelle parmi mon peuple et chacun sera libre de "
"rejoindre les Sentinelles. Non seulement tu as gagné l'estime des elfes et "
"des nains, mais tu as aussi mérité le respect des dracans. Je gage que de "
"nombreux seront ceux qui s'allieront à ta cause."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:517
msgid ""
"If you are ever in desperate need of help then come to us. The gryphons will "
"show you the way."
msgstr ""
"Si jamais tu as désespérément besoin d'aide, viens nous voir. Les griffons "
"te montreront le chemin."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:522
msgid "Thanks, friend."
msgstr "Merci, mon ami."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:535
msgid "Alfred, your assistance has also been a great help to us."
msgstr "Alfred, vous aussi, vous nous avez été d'un grand secours."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:540
msgid ""
"Pah, think nothing of it. It will sure make an interesting story to tell the "
"folks back home."
msgstr ""
"Peuh ! N'y pensez plus. Ça fera sûrement une bonne histoire à raconter de "
"retour à la maison."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:545
msgid "So you would like to return to your home?"
msgstr "Alors, vous désirez rentrer chez vous ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:550
msgid ""
"Yes. The dead should stay in the land of the dead. It is against the laws of "
"nature for it to be otherwise. There is just one problem; Malifor forced me "
"into this body and I don't know how to get out of it."
msgstr ""
"Oui. Les morts doivent rester au royaume des morts. Il est contre-nature "
"qu'il en soit autrement. Il y a juste un problème. Malifor m'a forcé à "
"habiter ce corps et je ne sais pas comment m'en dépouiller."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:555
msgid ""
"I believe Theta and I can help you with that, Alfred. Have no worries, you "
"shall soon be home."
msgstr ""
"Theta et moi pouvons probablement faire quelque chose pour vous, Alfred. "
"N'ayez crainte, vous serez bientôt de retour chez vous."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:560
msgid ""
"Thank you father, and thank you again, Tallin for all that you have done, "
"both for the world of the living and the dead."
msgstr ""
"Merci mon père, et merci encore, Tallin, pour tout ce que vous avez "
"accompli, pour les vivants comme pour les morts."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:565
msgid "My thanks to you as well, Alfred. May you rest in peace."
msgstr ""
"Acceptez aussi mes remerciement, Alfred. Puissiez-vous reposer en paix."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:572
msgid ""
"Ro'Arthian and Ro'Sothian, you two have also been of staunch allies. As per "
"our agreement, you may return to Highbrook Pass, and I will see to it that "
"guards are posted at both ends barring any who seek to enter without your "
"leave, on pain of death."
msgstr ""
"Ro'Arthian et Ro'Sothian, vous vous êtes montrés tous les deux des alliés "
"précieux. Selon les termes de notre accord, vous pouvez retourner au Col du "
"Haut-Rupt et je veillerai à ce que des gardes soient postés aux deux "
"entrées, interdisant à quiconque d'entrer, sous peine de mort."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Thank you, Tallin. Our old bones are weary of being animated long past their "
"time. Now we will finally be able to rest in peace. However, as we have "
"fought hard for this respite, we shall not allow our effort go to waste. "
"When the Northlands are in direst need of us, we shall rise once again."
msgstr ""
"Merci, Tallin. Nous sommes las de devoir bouger nos vieilles carcasses "
"depuis si longtemps. Nous allons enfin pouvoir reposer en paix. Mais comme "
"nous nous sommes battus avec acharnement pour mériter ce répit, nous ne "
"voudrions pas que notre effort fût vain. Quand les Terres du Nord auront "
"désespérément besoin de nous, nous nous lèverons à nouveau."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:588
msgid ""
"Stalrag, for years now we have fought each other, but recent events have "
"made us allies. I go now to eternal sleep; may we part as friends."
msgstr ""
"Stalrag, pendant des années nous nous sommes affrontés, mais les récents "
"événements ont fait de nous des alliés. Je vais maintenant trouver le repos "
"éternel. Puissions-nous nous quitter en amis."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:593
msgid "May your rest be peaceful and undisturbed, Ro'Arthian."
msgstr "Puisse ton repos être paisible et n'être jamais troublé, Ro'Arthian."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:606
msgid ""
"And Anita... I may be rash and bold to ask this but... *goes to his knees in "
"front of Anita and takes her hand* Will you marry me?"
msgstr ""
"Et Anita... Je vais peut-être paraître effronté et irréfléchi de demander "
"cela mais... *il s'agenouille devant Anita et prend sa main* Voulez-vous "
"m'épouser ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:611
msgid " *struck speechless*"
msgstr " *reste sans voix*"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:616
msgid ""
"Tallin, are you sure? Elves have a very long lifespan compared to humans. "
"She will live for at least another thousand years while you have hardly "
"seventy years ahead of you... at most."
msgstr ""
"Tallin, en es-tu sûr ? Les elfes ont une espérance de vie très longue "
"comparée aux humains. Elle vivra encore au moins mille ans alors qu'il te "
"reste à peine soixante-dix ans devant toi... au mieux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:621
msgid ""
" *eyes on Anita* I know, Hamel. Then may the coming seventy years be the "
"most happiest and fulfilling years in our lives. Should we deny ourselves "
"happiness out of the fear of loss?"
msgstr ""
" *les yeux fixés sur Anita* Je sais, Hamel. Alors puissent ces soixante-dix "
"années être les plus heureuses et épanouissantes de nos vies. Devrions-nous "
"dire non au bonheur par simple crainte de perdre l'être aimé ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:626
msgid "Well spoken!"
msgstr "Bien parlé !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:631
msgid "I may be foolish to say this, Tallin, but... yes."
msgstr "Je suis peut-être bête de dire cela, Tallin, mais... oui."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:636
msgid ""
"The joy of the multitude could not be contained, and the ensuing celebration "
"lasted for a full five days. At that time Tallin and Anita were duly married "
"by Father Marcus and Sister Theta."
msgstr ""
"La joie de l'assemblée ne put plus se contenir, et les fêtes qui "
"s'ensuivirent durèrent cinq jours entiers durant lesquels Tallin et Anita "
"furent mariés en bonne et due forme par Père Marcus et Sœur Theta."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:642
msgid ""
"After the wedding, Tallin and Anita went back to Dwarven Doors where they "
"founded the Couuncil of Warders of the Northern Alliance, a body dedicated "
"to ensuring peace and justice in the Northlands. It was soon settled that "
"the main headquarters of the Northern Alliance would be the new city of "
"Dwarven Doors."
msgstr ""
"Après la cérémonie, Tallin et Anita retournèrent aux Portes des Nains et y "
"fondèrent le Conseil des Sentinelles de l'Alliance du Nord, destiné à "
"maintenir la paix et la justice dans les Terres du Nord. Il fut vite décidé "
"d'établir le quartier général de l'Alliance du Nord dans la nouvelle cité "
"des Portes des Nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:648
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"On Father Marcus's advice, the Council approached all the different orcish "
"tribes and made treaties with them. If a chieftain refused to cooperate with "
"the Alliance, he was forcibly removed from his post and another more "
"favorably disposed put in his place."
msgstr ""
"Suivant les conseils de Père Marcus, le Conseil commença par contacter les "
"différentes tribus orcs et passer des accords avec elles. Si un seigneur de "
"guerre refusait de coopérer, il était destitué de force et un autre seigneur "
"de guerre, plus coopératif, prenait sa place."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:654
msgid ""
"Although Tallin faced many challenges as the head of the Northern Alliance, "
"his marriage with Anita was serene and filled with happiness. Together they "
"had one son, about whom were written many legends."
msgstr ""
"Tallin dut relever de nombreux défis en tant que chef de l'Alliance du Nord, "
"mais son mariage avec Anita fut paisible et très heureux. Ils eurent un fils "
"ensemble, à propos duquel on écrivit de nombreuses légendes."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:662
msgid ""
"Once again I thank all of you. For those of you who are leaving, may the "
"Lords of Light - or Darkness - guide you on your path. For those of you who "
"are staying - come, we have much to do."
msgstr ""
"Une fois encore, je vous remercie tous. Pour ceux qui partent, puissent les "
"Seigneurs de la Lumière - ou des Ténèbres - vous ouvrir la voie. Pour ceux "
"qui restent, venez, beaucoup de travail nous attend."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Thus, Tallin and his friends went back to Dwarven Doors where they founded "
"the Council of Warders of the Northern Alliance, a body dedicated to "
"ensuring peace and justice in the Northlands. It was soon settled that the "
"main headquarters of the Northern Alliance would be the new city of Dwarven "
"Doors."
msgstr ""
"C'est ainsi que Tallin et ses amis retournèrent aux Portes des Nains où ils "
"fondèrent le Conseil des Sentinelles de l'Alliance du Nord, destiné à "
"assurer la paix et la justice dans les Terres du Nord. Il fut vite décidé "
"d'établir le quartier général de l'Alliance du Nord dans la nouvelle cité "
"des Portes des Nains."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:673
msgid ""
"On Father Marcus's advice, the Council approached all the different orcish "
"tribes and made treaties with them. If a chieftain refused to cooperate with "
"the Allience, he was be forcibly removed from his post and another more "
"favorably disposed put in his place."
msgstr ""
"Suivant les conseils de Père Marcus, le Conseil commença par contacter les "
"différentes tribus orcs et passer des accords avec elles. Si un seigneur de "
"guerre refusait de coopérer, il était destitué de force et un autre seigneur "
"de guerre, plus coopératif, prenait sa place."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:681
msgid ""
"In time, Knalga's caverns were refurbished, becoming a busy and prosperous "
"home to many dwarves. Under the protection of the Northern Alliance, people "
"of all races began coming, as they did before, from all corners of the known "
"- and unknown - world to trade with the Dwarves of Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Les cavernes de Knalga furent progressivement remplies et devinrent un "
"refuge actif et prospère pour de nombreux nains. Sous la protection de "
"l'Alliance du Nord, des peuples de toutes races affluèrent, comme "
"auparavant, de tous les coins du monde connu - et inconnu - pour commercer "
"avec les Nains de Knalga."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:687
msgid ""
"Thus, from a small, enslaved community, the people of Dwarven Doors - by "
"their fortitude, valor, and wisdom - brought the Northlands out of the "
"darkness and restored them to their former glory."
msgstr ""
"Ainsi, à partir d'une petite communauté d'esclaves, le peuple des Portes des "
"Nains, par son courage, son intelligence et sa bravoure, sortit les Terres "
"du Nord du chaos et restaura leur gloire passée."

