msgid "No, Stalrag! Without you what will become of the Shinsplitters?"
msgstr "Stalrag, non ! Sans toi, qu'adviendra-t-il des Brisetibias ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:134
msgid ""
"Shinsplitters... join Tallin.... He is your new.... leader.... trust..... "
"and..... serve..... him.... as.... you...... have.....served....me."
msgstr ""
"Brisetibias... unissez-vous à Tallin.... Il est votre... nouveau... chef.... "
"Soyez-lui... fidèles... et... servez-le... aussi bien... que... vous... "
"m'avez... servi."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:139
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your death shall not go unavenged, brave Stalrag. DEATH TO THE ORCS!!!"
msgstr "Votre mort ne sera pas impunie, vaillant Stalrag. MORT AUX ORCS !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:144
msgid "DIE, YOU FOUL SCUM!!!"
msgstr "MOUREZ, SALES VERMINES !!!"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Argh! I am finished, but our campaign must... not end... crush..... our..... "
"enemies ..... and ..... save..... our...... people......."
msgstr ""
