#, fuzzy
msgid " *rolls eyes* Dramatic as always."
msgstr "*roule les yeux* Elle en fait trop, comme d'habitude."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:286
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Theta, when this is all over, you should paint your face and join a theater."
msgstr ""
