msgid " *giggle* Thank you honey."
msgstr "Héhéhéhé, merci mamour."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:354
#, fuzzy
msgid "Thank the lords of light, not me!"
msgstr "Remercie les seigneurs de la lumière, pas moi !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:373
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:665
msgid "You incompetent fools, you think you can kill us? Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Bande d'idiots incapables ! Vous croyez pouvoir nous tuer ? Bonne chance !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:395
#, fuzzy
