#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:409
msgid "Ack! Stupid slobbering beast!"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:414
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your efforts to destroy us are in vain, you foul creature."
msgstr "Tes efforts pour nous détruire sont vains, créature putride !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:435
msgid "There we go, payback time!"
