#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:454
msgid "Failed? Never! The word failure is not in our dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Échoué ? Jamais ! Le mot échec ne fait pas partie de notre dictionnaire."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:475
msgid "There we go, let's give this one more shot!"
msgstr "C'est parti, on remet ça !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:479
msgid "Just try not to kill yourself again."
msgstr "Essaie juste de ne pas encore te faire tuer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:493
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Alas! I am dying! Marcus darling, I wish you were beside me so that I may "
"die in your arms! So that I may feel the kiss of your lips on mine one last "
"time!"
msgstr ""
"Hélas ! Je me meurs ! Marcus chéri, j'aurais aimé t'avoir à mes côtés pour "
"mourir dans tes bras ! Pour sentir tes lèvres sur les miennes une toute "
"dernière fois !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:498
msgid " *rolls eyes* Theta, do you always have to be so dramatic?"
msgstr ""
"*roule les yeux* Theta, pourquoi faut-il que tu sois toujours aussi "
"théâtrale ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:508
#, fuzzy
msgid "Um..... Father? Your wife just got killed..."
msgstr "Hum... Père ? Votre femme vient d'être tuée..."

# Mais qu'espère-t-il si elle est déjà morte ? À corriger.
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:513
#, fuzzy
msgid "Oh right. I CALL UPON THE LORDS OF LIGHT TO GRANT YOU LIFE!"
msgstr ""
"Oh oui, bien sûr. J'INVOQUE LES SEIGNEURS DE LUMIÈRE ! QU'ILS PRÉSERVENT TA "
"VIE !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:534
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Theta, you should know by now that it is very unclerical to make such a "
"spectacle of yourself."
msgstr ""
"Theta, tu devrais pourtant savoir que c'est très sacrilège de faire de "
"telles manières en public."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:538
msgid "Come on, honey! Those were my dying words, after all!"
msgstr ""
"Mais enfin, chéri ! C'étaient tout de même mes derniers mots avant "
"d'expirer !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:542
msgid " *rolls eyes* Women!"
msgstr "*roule les yeux* Ah, les femmes !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:556
msgid ""
"You cruel creature! How dare you use your brute strength against such a "
"frail creature as me."
msgstr ""
"Vile créature ! Comment oses-tu user de ta force brutale contre une frêle "
"créature comme moi ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:561
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Don't worry, Theta, you will have plenty of opportunities to set him "
"straight."
msgstr ""
"Ne t'en fais pas Theta, tu auras de nombreuses occasions pour l'éduquer."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:582
msgid "That's darned right!"
msgstr "C'est foutrement vrai !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:587
msgid ""
"Theta! Language like that coming from you! You should really stop hanging "
"around the dwarves so much."
msgstr ""
"Theta ! De tels mots venant de toi ! Tu devrais vraiment arrêter de traîner "
"tout le temps avec les nains."

# À améliorer selon le contexte
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:615
#, fuzzy
msgid "Alas! So.... close."
msgstr "Hélas ! Si... près."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:620
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hey, that's not right. The good guys aren't supposed to die. Oh well, I'll "
"fix that."
msgstr ""
"Hé, ce n'est pas juste ! Les gentils ne sont pas censés mourir. Tant pis, je "
"vais arranger ça."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:646
msgid "Ahh yes, that's better."
msgstr "Ah oui, c'est mieux."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:686
msgid "Ouch! That hurt. Let's try not to do that again ok?"
msgstr "Ouïe, ça fait mal. Essayons de ne pas recommencer, d'accord ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:705
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh dear. Did you just go and get yourself killed again, Marcus? Well, I'll "
"fix that."
msgstr ""
"Oh mon dieu. Tu es encore allé te faire tuer, Marcus ? Bon, je vais arranger "
"ça."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:726
msgid "Marcus! You bad boy, always getting into trouble."
msgstr ""
"Marcus ! Tout le temps en train de t'attirer des ennuis, petit garnement."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:730
msgid "Sorry, won't do it again. Promise!"
msgstr "Pardon, j'le ferai plus, promis !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:744
msgid "The forces of good can never be defeated by the likes of you!"
msgstr ""
"Les forces du bien ne sauraient être défaites par les individus de ton "
"espèce !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:749
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yeah, try taking a bath and you MIGHT be able to kill him for good *wink "
"wink*. But for the time being, abracadabra!"
msgstr ""
"Ouais, essaie de prendre un bain et tu pourrais PEUT-ÊTRE le tuer pour de "
"bon *clin d'œil amusé*. Mais pour l'instant, HOLA !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:770
msgid "I heard that, Theta."
msgstr "J'ai entendu, Theta."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:774
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hey, just trying to give him an incentive to drown himself."
msgstr "Hé, je voulais juste le pousser à se noyer tout seul."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:793
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Stupid troll, maybe next time you should try killing someone who can be "
"killed."
msgstr ""
"Stupide Troll, peut-être devrais-tu essayer de tuer quelqu'un qui puisse "
"mourir la prochaine fois."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:823
msgid "Argh! I'll just come back and finish you in my next life."
msgstr "Argh ! Je reviendrai et en finirai avec toi dans ma prochaine vie."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:828
msgid "Which might be sooner then you think."
msgstr "Ce qui arrivera peut-être plus tôt que tu ne le penses."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:849
msgid "See?"
msgstr "Tu vois ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:853
msgid "Now where did he go!?"
msgstr "Où est-il passé ?"

