msgid ""
"Geez Theta, don't you think that this isn't really a good time to talk about "
"that?"
msgstr ""
"Miséricorde, Theta ! Tu crois vraiment que c'est le bon moment pour parler "
"de ça ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:908
msgid " *giggle* Sorry!"
msgstr " *gloussements* Désolée."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:932
msgid " Alas! My wanderings have come to an end."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:937
msgid "Blast it, we have lost a valuable ally."
msgstr "Malédiction, nous avons perdu un précieux allié."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:942
msgid "Farewell Elenia. May you find peace in your final journey."
msgstr ""
"Adieu Elenia. Puisses-tu trouver la paix à l'issue de ce dernier voyage."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:959
msgid " Wha... how can this happen?"
msgstr "Mais... mais... comment est-ce possible ?"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/herodeaths.cfg:964
msgid "He was stark raving mad, but I am sure going to miss him."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/utils.cfg:193
msgid ""
"You invaded my kingdom, drove me from my mines, raided my dungeon, and "
"plundered my treasury Your audacity ends here!"
msgstr ""
"Tu envahis mon royaume, me chasse de mes mines, vide mes geôles et pille ma "
"trésorerie. Ton audace s'arrête ici !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/utils.cfg:198
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You are wrong, Malifor, for you shall be the one who is destroyed. You are "
"cruel, merciless and a terror to all that lives. The world will be a better "
"place with you gone!"
msgstr ""
"Tu te trompes Malifor, car c'est ta vie qui va s'arrêter ici. Tu es cruel et "
"impitoyable, et tu terrorises tout ce qui vit. Le monde ne te regrettera "
"pas !"

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/utils.cfg:203
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To feed your greed and hunger you have terrorized all that is good. You have "
"disturbed the rest of the brave defenders of Knalga. Now, your evil reign "
"shall be brought to an end."
msgstr ""
"Pour des fins égoïstes, tu as terrorisé tout ce qui est bon. Tu as troublé "
"le repos des braves défenseurs de Knalga. Ton règne abominable s'achève "
"désormais."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/utils/utils.cfg:208
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fools! Don't think it's so easy to kill me. Your corpses shall all soon be "
"serving me. Fall on them, my hordes!"
msgstr ""
"Idiots ! Ne me croyez pas si facile à tuer. Vos cadavres seront bientôt sous "
"mon commandement. Anéantissez-les, mes créatures !"

